quran[842]{c,v,t}:
  37,1,WE ES-SAFFATI SEFFÆN
  37,2,FALZZAXHIRATI ZEXHRÆN
  37,3,FALTTALIJATI DHIKRÆN
  37,4,‘INNE ‘ILEHEKUM LEWAHIDUN
  37,5,REBBU ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI WE MA BEJNEHUMA WE REBBUL-MESHARIKI
  37,6,‘INNA ZEJJENNA ES-SEMA’E ED-DUNJA BIZINETINL-KEWAKIB
  37,7,WE HIFDHÆN MIN KULLI SHEJTANIN MARIDIN
  37,8,LA JESSEMMA’UNE ‘ILAL-MELE’IL-’A’LA WE JUKDHEFUNE MIN KULLI XHANIBIN
  37,9,DUHURÆN WE LEHUM ‘ADHABUN WE ESIBUN
  37,10,‘ILLA MEN HATIFEL-HATFETE FE’ETBE’AHU SHIHABUN THAKIBUNA
  37,11,FASTEFTIHIM ‘EHUM ‘ESHEDDU HALKÆN ‘EM MEN HALEKNA ‘INNA HALEKNAHUM MIN TININ LAZIBIN
  37,12,BEL ‘AXHIBTE WE JESHARUNE
  37,13,WE ‘IDHA DHUKKIRU LA JEDHKURUNE
  37,14,WE ‘IDHA RE’EW ‘AJETEN JESTESHIRUNE
  37,15,WE KALU ‘IN HADHA ‘ILLA SIHRUN MUBINUN
  37,16,‘E’IDHA MITNA WE KUNNA TURABÆN WE ‘IDHAMÆN ‘E’INNA LEMEB’UTHUNE
  37,17,‘EWE’ABA’UUNAL-’EWWELUNE
  37,18,KUL NE’AM WE ‘ENTUM DAHIRUNE
  37,19,FE’INNEMA HIJE ZEXHRETUN WAHIDETUN FE’IDHA HUM JENDHURUNE
  37,20,WE KALU JA WEJLENA HADHA JEWMU ED-DINI
  37,21,HADHA JEWMUL-FESLIL-LEDHI KUNTUM BIHI TUKEDHDHIBUNE
  37,22,EHSHURUL-LEDHINE DHELEMU WE ‘EZWAXHEHUM WE MA KANU JA’BUDUNE
  37,23,MIN DUNI ELLAHI FAHDUHUM ‘ILA SIRATIL-XHEHIMI
  37,24,WE KIFUHUM ‘INNEHUM MES’ULUNE
  37,25,MA LEKUM LA TENASERUNE
  37,26,BEL HUMUL-JEWME MUSTESLIMUNE
  37,27,WE ‘EKBELE BA’DUHUM ‘ALA BA’DIN JETESA’ELUNE
  37,28,KALU ‘INNEKUM KUNTUM TE’TUNENA ‘ANIL-JEMINI
  37,29,KALU BEL LEM TEKUNU MU’UMININE
  37,30,WE MA KANE LENA ‘ALEJKUM MIN SULTANIN BEL KUNTUM KAWMÆN TAGINE
  37,31,FEHEKKA ‘ALEJNA KAWLU RABBINA ‘INNA LEDHA’IKUNE
  37,32,FE’EGWEJNAKUM ‘INNA KUNNA GAWINE
  37,33,FE’INNEHUM JEWME’IDHIN FIL-’ADHABI MUSHTERIKUNE
  37,34,‘INNA KEDHALIKE NEF’ALU BIL-MUXHRIMINE
  37,35,‘INNEHUM KANU ‘IDHA KILE LEHUM LA ‘ILAHE ‘ILLALLAHU JESTEKBIRUNE
  37,36,WE JEKULUNE ‘E’INNA LETARIKU ‘ALIHETINA LISHA’IRIN MEXHNUNIN
  37,37,BEL XHA’E BIL-HEKKI WE SEDDEKAL-MURSELINE
  37,38,‘INNEKUM LEDHA’IKUL-’ADHABIL-’ELIMI
  37,39,WE MA TUXHZEWNE ‘ILLA MA KUNTUM TA’MELUNE
  37,40,‘ILLA ‘IBADEL-LAHIL-MUHLESINE
  37,41,‘ULA’IKE LEHUM RIZKUN MA’LUMUN
  37,42,FEWAKIHU WE HUM MUKREMUNE
  37,43,FI XHENNATI EN-NA’IMI
  37,44,‘ALA SURURIN MUTEKABILINE
  37,45,JUTAFU ‘ALEJHIM BIKE’SIN MIN MA’ININ
  37,46,BEJDA’E LEDHDHETIN LILSHSHARIBINE
  37,47,LA FIHA GAWLUN WE LA HUM ‘ANHA JUNZEFUNE
  37,48,WE ‘INDEHUM KASIRATUT-TERFI ‘INUN
  37,49,KE’ENNEHUNNE BEJDUN MEKNUNUN
  37,50,FE’EKBELE BA’DUHUM ‘ALA BA’DIN JETESA’ELUNE
  37,51,KALE KA’ILUN MINHUM ‘INNI KANE LI KARINUN
  37,52,JEKULU ‘E’INNEKE LEMINEL-MUSEDDIKINE
  37,53,‘E’IDHA MITNA WE KUNNA TURABÆN WE ‘IDHAMÆN ‘E’INNA LEMEDINUNE
  37,54,KALE HEL ‘ENTUM MUTTELI’UNE
  37,55,FATTELE’A FERE’AHU FI SEWA’IL-XHEHIMI
  37,56,KALE TE-ELLAHI ‘IN KIDTE LETURDINI
  37,57,WE LEWLA NI’METU RABBI LEKUNTU MINEL-MUHDERINE
  37,58,‘EFEMA NEHNU BIMEJJITINE
  37,59,‘ILLA MEWTETENAL-’ULA WE MA NEHNU BIMU’ADHDHEBINE
  37,60,‘INNE HADHA LEHUWEL-FEWZUL-’ADHIMU
  37,61,LIMITHLI HADHA FELJA’MELIL-’AMILUNE
  37,62,‘EDHELIKE HAJRUN NUZULÆN ‘EM SHEXHERETU EZ-ZEKKUMI
  37,63,‘INNA XHE’ALNAHA FITNETEN LILDHDHALIMINE
  37,64,‘INNEHA SHEXHERETUN TEHRUXHU FI ‘ESLIL-XHEHIMI
  37,65,TEL’UHA KE’ENNEHU RU’USU ESH-SHEJATINI
  37,66,FE’INNEHUM LE’AKILUNE MINHA FEMALI’UNE MINHAL-BUTUNE
  37,67,THUMME ‘INNE LEHUM ‘ALEJHA LESHEWBÆN MIN HEMIMIN
  37,68,THUMME ‘INNE MERXHI’AHUM LE’ILAL-XHEHIMI
  37,69,‘INNEHUM ‘ELFEW ‘ABA’EHUM DALLINE
  37,70,FEHUM ‘ALA ‘ATHARIHIM JUHRA’UNE
  37,71,WE LEKAD DELLE KABLEHUM ‘EKTHERUL-’EWWELINE
  37,72,WE LEKAD ‘ERSELNA FIHIM MUNDHIRINE
  37,73,FANDHUR KEJFE KANE ‘AKIBETUL-MUNDHERINE
  37,74,‘ILLA ‘IBADEL-LAHIL-MUHLESINE
  37,75,WE LEKAD NADANA NUHUN FELENI’MEL-MUXHIBUNE
  37,76,WE NEXHXHEJNAHU WE ‘EHLEHU MINEL-KERBIL-’ADHIMI
  37,77,WE XHE’ALNA DHURRIJETEHU HUMUL-BAKINE
  37,78,WE TEREKNA ‘ALEJHI FIL-’AHIRINE
  37,79,SELAMUN ‘ALA NUHIN FIL-’ALEMINE
  37,80,‘INNA KEDHALIKE NEXHZIL-MUHSININE
  37,81,‘INNEHU MIN ‘IBADINAL-MU’UMININE
  37,82,THUMME ‘EGREKNAL-’AHARINE
  37,83,WE ‘INNE MIN SHI’ATIHI LE’IBRAHIME
  37,84,‘IDH XHA’E REBBEHU BIKALBIN SELIMIN
  37,85,‘IDH KALE LI’EBIHI WE KAWMIHI MADHA TA’BUDUNE
  37,86,‘E’IFKÆN ‘ALIHETEN DUNEL-LAHI TURIDUNE
  37,87,FEMA DHENNUKUM BIREBBIL-’ALEMINE
  37,88,FENEDHERE NEDHRETEN FI EN-NUXHUMI
  37,89,FEKALE ‘INNI SEKIMUN
  37,90,FETEWELLEW ‘ANHU MUDBIRINE
  37,91,FERAGA ‘ILA ‘ALIHETIHIM FEKALE ‘ELA TE’KULUNE
  37,92,MA LEKUM LA TENTIKUNE
  37,93,FERAGA ‘ALEJHIM DERBÆN BIL-JEMINI
  37,94,FE’EKBELU ‘ILEJHI JEZIFFUNE
  37,95,KALE ‘ETA’BUDUNE MA TENHITUNE
  37,96,WEL-LAHU HALEKAKUM WE MA TA’MELUNE
  37,97,KALU EBNU LEHU BUNJANÆN FE’ELKUHU FIL-XHEHIMI
  37,98,FE’ERADU BIHI KEJDÆN FEXHE’ALNAHUMUL-’ESFELINE
  37,99,WE KALE ‘INNI DHAHIBUN ‘ILA RABBI SEJEHDINI
  37,100,REBBI HEB LI MINE ES-SALIHINE
  37,101,FEBESHSHERNAHU BIGULAMIN HELIMIN
  37,102,FELEMMA BELEGA ME’AHU ES-SA’JE KALE JA BUNEJJE ‘INNI ‘ERA FIL-MENAMI ‘ENNI ‘EDHBEHUKE FANDHUR MADHA TERA KALE JA ‘EBETI EF’AL MA TU’UMERU SETEXHIDUNI ‘IN SHA’EL-LAHU MINE ES-SABIRINE
  37,103,FELEMMA ‘ESLEMA WE TELLEHU LILXHEBINI
  37,104,WE NADEJNAHU ‘EN JA ‘IBRAHIMU
  37,105,KAD SEDDEKTE ER-RU’UJA ‘INNA KEDHALIKE NEXHZIL-MUHSININE
  37,106,‘INNE HADHA LEHUWEL-BELA’UL-MUBINU
  37,107,WE FEDEJNAHU BIDHIBHIN ‘ADHIMIN
  37,108,WE TEREKNA ‘ALEJHI FIL-’AHIRINE
  37,109,SELAMUN ‘ALA ‘IBRAHIME
  37,110,KEDHALIKE NEXHZIL-MUHSININE
  37,111,‘INNEHU MIN ‘IBADINAL-MU’UMININE
  37,112,WE BESHSHERNAHU BI’ISHAKA NEBIJÆN MINE ES-SALIHINE
  37,113,WE BAREKNA ‘ALEJHI WE ‘ALA ‘ISHAKA WE MIN DHURRIJETIHIMA MUHSINUN WE DHALIMUN LINEFSIHI MUBINUN
  37,114,WE LEKAD MENENNA ‘ALA MUSA WE HARUNE
  37,115,WE NEXHXHEJNAHUMA WE KAWMEHUMA MINEL-KERBIL-’ADHIMI
  37,116,WE NESERNAHUM FEKANU HUMUL-GALIBINE
  37,117,WE ‘ATEJNAHUMAL-KITABEL-MUSTEBINE
  37,118,WE HEDEJNAHUMA ES-SIRATEL-MUSTEKIME
  37,119,WE TEREKNA ‘ALEJHIMA FIL-’AHIRINE
  37,120,SELAMUN ‘ALA MUSA WE HARUNE
  37,121,‘INNA KEDHALIKE NEXHZIL-MUHSININE
  37,122,‘INNEHUMA MIN ‘IBADINAL-MU’UMININE
  37,123,WE ‘INNE ‘ILJASE LEMINEL-MURSELINE
  37,124,‘IDH KALE LIKAWMIHI ‘ELA TETTEKUNE
  37,125,‘ETED’UNE BA’LÆN WE TEDHERUNE ‘EHSENEL-HALIKINE
  37,126,ELLAHE REBBEKUM WE REBBE ‘ABA’IKUMUL-’EWWELINE
  37,127,FEKEDHDHEBUHU FE’INNEHUM LEMUHDERUNE
  37,128,‘ILLA ‘IBADEL-LAHIL-MUHLESINE
  37,129,WE TEREKNA ‘ALEJHI FIL-’AHIRINE
  37,130,SELAMUN ‘ALA ‘IL JA -SIN
  37,131,‘INNA KEDHALIKE NEXHZIL-MUHSININE
  37,132,‘INNEHU MIN ‘IBADINAL-MU’UMININE
  37,133,WE ‘INNE LUTÆN LEMINEL-MURSELINE
  37,134,‘IDH NEXHXHEJNAHU WE ‘EHLEHU ‘EXHMA’INE
  37,135,‘ILLA ‘AXHUZÆN FIL-GABIRINE
  37,136,THUMME DEMMERNAL-’AHARINE
  37,137,WE ‘INNEKUM LETEMURRUNE ‘ALEJHIM MUSBIHINE
  37,138,WE BIL-LEJLI ‘EFELA TA’KILUNE
  37,139,WE ‘INNE JUNIS LEMINEL-MURSELINE
  37,140,‘IDH ‘EBEKA ‘ILAL-FULKIL-MESHHUNI
  37,141,FESAHEME FEKANE MINEL-MUDHEDINE
  37,142,FALTEKAMEHUL-HUTU WE HUWE MULIMUN
  37,143,FELEWLA ‘ENNEHU KANE MINEL-MUSEBBIHINE
  37,144,LELEBITHE FI BETNIHI ‘ILA JEWMI JUB’ATHUNE
  37,145,FENEBEDHNAHU BIL-’ARA’I WE HUWE SEKIMUN
  37,146,WE ‘ENBETNA ‘ALEJHI SHEXHERETEN MIN JEKTININ
  37,147,WE ‘ERSELNAHU ‘ILA MIA’ETI ‘ELFIN ‘EW JEZIDUNE
  37,148,FE’AMENU FEMETTA’NAHUM ‘ILA HININ
  37,149,FASTEFTIHIM ‘ELIREBBIKEL-BENATU WE LEHUMUL-BENUNE
  37,150,‘EM HALEKNAL-MELA’IKETE ‘INATHÆN WE HUM SHAHIDUNE
  37,151,‘ELA ‘INNEHUM MIN ‘IFKIHIM LEJEKULUNE
  37,152,WELEDEL-LAHU WE ‘INNEHUM LEKADHIBUNE
  37,153,‘ASTEFAL-BENATI ‘ALEL-BENINE
  37,154,MA LEKUM KEJFE TEHKUMUNE
  37,155,‘EFELA TEDHEKKERUN
  37,156,‘EM LEKUM SULTANUN MUBINUN
  37,157,FE’TU BIKITABIKUM ‘IN KUNTUM SADIKINE
  37,158,WE XHE’ALU BEJNEHU WE BEJNEL-XHINNETI NESEBÆN WE LEKAD ‘ALIMETIL-XHINNETU ‘INNEHUM LEMUHDERUNE
  37,159,SUBHANEL-LAHI ‘AMMA JESIFUNE
  37,160,‘ILLA ‘IBADEL-LAHIL-MUHLESINE
  37,161,FE’INNEKUM WE MA TA’BUDUNE
  37,162,MA ‘ENTUM ‘ALEJHI BIFATININE
  37,163,‘ILLA MEN HUWE SALIL-XHEHIMI
  37,164,WE MA MINNA ‘ILLA LEHU MEKAMUN MA’LUMUN
  37,165,WE ‘INNA LENEHNU ES-SAFFUNE
  37,166,WE ‘INNA LENEHNUL-MUSEBBIHUNE
  37,167,WE ‘IN KANU LEJEKULUNE
  37,168,LEW ‘ENNE ‘INDENA DHIKRÆN MINEL-’EWWELINE
  37,169,LEKUNNA ‘IBADEL-LAHIL-MUHLESINE
  37,170,FEKEFERU BIHI FESEWFE JA’LEMUNE
  37,171,WE LEKAD SEBEKAT KELIMETUNA LI’IBADINAL-MURSELIN
  37,172,‘INNEHUM LEHUMUL-MENSURUNE
  37,173,WE ‘INNE XHUNDENA LEHUMUL-GALIBUNE
  37,174,FETEWELLE ‘ANHUM HETTA HININ
  37,175,WE ‘EBSIRHUM FESEWFE JUBSIRUNE
  37,176,‘EFEBI’ADHABINA JESTA’XHILUNE
  37,177,FE’IDHA NEZELE BISAHETIHIM FESA’E SEBAHUL-MUNDHERINE
  37,178,WE TEWELLE ‘ANHUM HETTA HININ
  37,179,WE ‘EBSIR FESEWFE JUBSIRUNE
  37,180,SUBHANE RABBIKE RABBIL-’IZZETI ‘AMMA JESIFUNE
  37,181,WE SELAMUN ‘ALEL-MURSELINE
  37,182,WEL-HEMDU LILLAHI RABBIL-’ALEMINE
  38,1,SAD WEL-KUR’ANI DHI EDH-DHIKRI
  38,2,BELIL-LEDHINE KEFERU FI ‘IZZETIN WE SHIKAKIN
  38,3,KEM ‘EHLEKNA MIN KABLIHIM MIN KARNIN FENADEW WELATE HINE MENASIN
  38,4,WE ‘AXHIBU ‘EN XHA’EHUM MUNDHIRUN MINHUM WE KALEL-KAFIRUNE HADHA SAHIRUN KEDHDHABUN
  38,5,‘EXHE’ALEL-’ALIHETE ‘ILEHÆN WAHIDÆN ‘INNE HADHA LESHEJ’UN ‘UXHABUN
  38,6,WE ENTELEKAL-MELE’U MINHUM ‘ENI EMSHU WE ESBIRU ‘ALA ‘ALIHETIKUM ‘INNE HADHA LESHEJ’UN JURADU
  38,7,MA SEMI’NA BIHEDHA FIL-MILLETIL-’AHIRETI ‘IN HADHA ‘ILLA EHTILAKUN
  38,8,‘E’UUNZILE ‘ALEJHI EDH-DHIKRU MIN BEJNINA BEL HUM FI SHEKKIN MIN DHIKRI BEL LEMMA JEDHUKU ‘ADHABI
  38,9,‘EM ‘INDEHUM HAZA’INU REHMETI RABBIKEL-’AZIZIL-WEHHABI
  38,10,‘EM LEHUM MULKU ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI WE MA BEJNEHUMA FELJERTEKU FIL-’ESBABI
  38,11,XHUNDUN MA HUNALIKE MEHZUMUN MINEL-’EHZABI
  38,12,KEDHDHEBET KABLEHUM KAWMU NUHIN WE ‘ADUN WE FIR’AWNU DHUL-’EWTADI
  38,13,WE THEMUDU WE KAWMU LUTIN WE ‘ESHABUL-’EJKETI ‘ULA’IKEL-’EHZABU
  38,14,‘IN KULLUN ‘ILLA KEDHDHEBE ER-RUSULE FEHEKKA ‘IKABI
  38,15,WE MA JENDHURU HA’UULA’ ‘ILLA SEJHETEN WAHIDETEN MA LEHA MIN FEWAKIN
  38,16,WE KALU REBBENA ‘AXHXHIL LENA KITTENA KABLE JEWMIL-HISABI
  38,17,ESBIR ‘ALA MA JEKULUNE WE EDHKUR ‘ABDENA DAWUDE DHAL-’EJDI ‘INNEHU ‘EWWABUN
  38,18,‘INNA SEHHARNAL-XHIBALE ME’AHU JUSEBBIHNE BIL-’ASHIJI WEL-’ISHRAKI
  38,19,WET-TEJRE MEHSHURETEN KULLUN LEHU ‘EWWABUN
  38,20,WE SHEDEDNA MULKEHU WE ‘ATEJNAHUL-HIKMETE WE FESLEL-HITABI
  38,21,WE HEL ‘ETAKE NEBE’UL-HASMI ‘IDH TESEWWERUL-MIHRABE
  38,22,‘IDH DEHALU ‘ALA DAWUDE FEFEZI’A MINHUM KALU LA TEHAF HASMANI BEGA BA’DUNA ‘ALA BA’DIN FAHKUM BEJNENA BIL-HEKKI WE LA TUSHTIT WE EHDINA ‘ILA SEWA’I ES-SIRATI
  38,23,‘INNE HADHA ‘EHI LEHU TIS’UN WE TIS’UNE NA’XHETEN WE LIJE NA’XHETUN WAHIDETUN FEKALE ‘EKFILNIHA WE ‘AZZENI FIL-HITABI
  38,24,KALE LEKAD DHELEMEKE BISU’UALI NA’XHETIKE ‘ILA NI’AXHIHI WE ‘INNE KETHIRÆN MINEL-HULETA’I LEJEBGI BA’DUHUM ‘ALA BA’DIN ‘ILLAL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU WE ‘AMILU ES-SALIHATI WE KALILUN MA HUM WE DHENNE DAWUDU ‘ENNEMA FETENNAHU FASTEGFERE REBBEHU WE HARRE RAKI’ÆN WE
  38,25,FEGAFERNA LEHU DHALIKE WE ‘INNE LEHU ‘INDENA LEZULFA WE HUSNE ME’ABIN
  38,26,JA DAWUDU ‘INNA XHE’ALNAKE HALIFETEN FIL-’ERDI FAHKUM BEJNE EN-NASI BIL-HEKKI WE LA TETTEBI’IL-HEWA FEJUDILLEKE ‘AN SEBILI ELLAHI ‘INNEL-LEDHINE JEDILLUNE ‘AN SEBILI ELLAHI LEHUM ‘ADHABUN SHEDIDUN BIMA NESU JEWMEL-HISABI
  38,27,WE MA HALEKNA ES-SEMA’E WEL-’ERDE WE MA BEJNEHUMA BATILÆN DHALIKE DHENNUL-LEDHINE KEFERU FEWEJLUN LILLEDHINE KEFERU MINE EN-NARI
  38,28,‘EM NEXH’ALUL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU WE ‘AMILU ES-SALIHATI KALMUFSIDINE FIL-’ERDI ‘EM NEXH’ALUL-MUTTEKINE KALFUXHXHARI
  38,29,KITABUN ‘ENZELNAHU ‘ILEJKE MUBAREKUN LIJEDDEBBERU ‘AJATIHI WE LIJETEDHEKKERE ‘ULUL-’ELBABI
  38,30,WE WEHEBNA LIDAWUDE SULEJMANE NI’MEL-’ABDU ‘INNEHU ‘EWWABUN
  38,31,‘IDH ‘URIDE ‘ALEJHI BIL-’ASHIJI ES-SAFINATUL-XHIJADU
  38,32,FEKALE ‘INNI ‘EHBEBTU HUBBEL-HAJRI ‘AN DHIKRI RABBI HETTA TEWARET BIL-HIXHABI
  38,33,RUDDUHA ‘ALEJJE FETEFIKA MESHÆN BIS-SUKI WEL-’A’NAKI
  38,34,WE LEKAD FETENNA SULEJMANE WE ‘ELKAJNA ‘ALA KURSIJIHI XHESEDÆN THUMME ‘ENABE
  38,35,KALE RABBI EGFIR LI WE HEB LI MULKÆN LA JENBEGI LI’HEDIN MIN BA’DI ‘INNEKE ‘ENTEL-WEHHABU
  38,36,FESEHHARNA LEHU ER-RIHE TEXHRI BI’EMRIHI RUHA’EN HEJTHU ‘ESABE
  38,37,WE ESH-SHEJATINE KULLE BENNA’IN WE GAWWASIN
  38,38,WE ‘AHARINE MUKARRENINE FIL-’ESFADI
  38,39,HADHA ‘ATA’UUNA FAMNUN ‘EW ‘EMSIK BIGAJRI HISABIN
  38,40,WE ‘INNE LEHU ‘INDENA LEZULFA WE HUSNE ME’ABIN
  38,41,WE EDHKUR ‘ABDENA ‘EJJUBE ‘IDH NADA REBBEHU ‘ENNI MESSENI ESH-SHEJTANU BINUSBIN WE ‘ADHABIN
  38,42,ERKUD BIRIXHLIKE HADHA MUGTESELUN BARIDUN WE SHERABUN
  38,43,WE WEHEBNA LEHU ‘EHLEHU WE MITHLEHUM ME’AHUM REHMETEN MINNA WE DHIKRA LI’WLIL-’ELBABI
  38,44,WE HUDH BIJEDIKE DIGTHÆN FADRIB BIHI WE LA TEHNETH ‘INNA WE XHEDNAHU SABIRÆN NI’MEL-’ABDU ‘INNEHU ‘EWWABUN
  38,45,WE EDHKUR ‘IBADENA ‘IBRAHIME WE ‘ISHAKA WE JA’KUBE ‘ULIL-’EJDI WEL-’EBSARI
  38,46,‘INNA ‘EHLESNAHUM BIHALISETIN DHIKRA ED-DARI
  38,47,WE ‘INNEHUM ‘INDENA LEMINEL-MUSTEFEJNEL-’EHJARI
  38,48,WE EDHKUR ‘ISMA’ILE WEL-JESE’A WE DHAL-KIFLI WE KULLUN MINEL-’EHJARI
  38,49,HADHA DHIKRUN WE ‘INNE LILMUTTEKINE LEHUSNE ME’ABIN
  38,50,XHENNATI ‘ADNIN MUFETTEHETEN LEHUMUL-’EBWABU
  38,51,MUTTEKI’INE FIHA JED’UNE FIHA BIFAKIHETIN KETHIRETIN WE SHERABIN
  38,52,WE ‘INDEHUM KASIRATUT-TERFI ‘ETRABUN
  38,53,HADHA MA TU’ADUNE LIJEWMIL-HISABI
  38,54,‘INNE HADHA LERIZKUNA MA LEHU MIN NEFADIN
  38,55,HADHA WE ‘INNE LILTTAGINE LESHERRE ME’ABIN
  38,56,XHEHENNEME JESLEWNEHA FEBI’SEL-MIHADU
  38,57,HADHA FELJEDHUKUHU HEMIMUN WE GASSAKUN
  38,58,WE ‘AHARU MIN SHEKLIHI ‘EZWAXHUN
  38,59,HADHA FEWXHUN MUKTEHIMUN ME’AKUM LA MERHEBÆN BIHIM ‘INNEHUM SALU EN-NARI
  38,60,KALU BEL ‘ENTUM LA MERHEBÆN BIKUM ‘ENTUM KADDEMTUMUHU LENA FEBI’SEL-KARARU
  38,61,KALU REBBENA MEN KADDEME LENA HADHA FEZID/HU ‘ADHABÆN DI’FÆN FI EN-NARI
  38,62,WE KALU MA LENA LA NERA RIXHALÆN KUNNA NA’UDDUHUM MINEL-’ESHRAR
  38,63,‘ATTEHADHNAHUM SIHRIJÆN ‘EM ZAGAT ‘ANHUMUL-’EBSARU
  38,64,‘INNE DHALIKE LEHEKKUN TEHASUMU ‘EHLI EN-NARI
  38,65,KUL ‘INNEMA ‘ENA MUNDHIRUN WE MA MIN ‘ILEHIN ‘ILLALLAHUL-WAHIDUL-KAHHARU
  38,66,REBBU ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI WE MA BEJNEHUMAL-’AZIZUL-GAFFARU
  38,67,KUL HUWE NEBE’UN ‘ADHIMUN
  38,68,‘ENTUM ‘ANHU MU’RIDUNE
  38,69,MA KANE LIJE MIN ‘ILMIN BIL-MELE’IL-’A’LA ‘IDH JEHTESIMUNE
  38,70,‘IN JUHA ‘ILEJJE ‘ILLA ‘ENNEMA ‘ENA NEDHIRUN MUBINUN
  38,71,‘IDH KALE REBBUKE LILMELA’IKETI ‘INNI HALIKUN BESHERÆN MIN TININ
  38,72,FE’IDHA SEWWEJTUHU WE NEFEHTU FIHI MIN RUHI FEKA’U LEHU SAXHIDINE
  38,73,FESEXHEDEL-MELA’IKETU KULLUHUM ‘EXHMA’UNE
  38,74,‘ILLA ‘IBLISE ESTEKBERE WE KANE MINEL-KAFIRINE
  38,75,KALE JA ‘IBLISU MA MENE’AKE ‘EN TESXHUDE LIMA HALEKTU BIJEDEJJE ‘ASTEKBERTE ‘EM KUNTE MINEL-’ALINE
  38,76,KALE ‘ENA HAJRUN MINHU HALEKTENI MIN NARIN WE HALEKTEHU MIN TININ
  38,77,KALE FAHRUXH MINHA FE’INNEKE REXHIMUN
  38,78,WE ‘INNE ‘ALEJKE LA’NETI ‘ILA JEWMI ED-DINI
  38,79,KALE RABBI FE’ENDHIRNI ‘ILA JEWMI JUB’ATHUNE
  38,80,KALE FE’INNEKE MINEL-MUNDHERINE
  38,81,‘ILA JEWMIL-WEKTIL-MA’LUMI
  38,82,KALE FEBI’IZZETIKE LE’UGWIJENNEHUM ‘EXHMA’INE
  38,83,‘ILLA ‘IBADEKE MINHUMUL-MUHLESINE
  38,84,KALE FALHEKKU WEL-HEKKA ‘EKULU
  38,85,LE’EMLE’ENNE XHEHENNEME MINKE WE MIMMEN TEBI’AKE MINHUM ‘EXHMA’INE
  38,86,KUL MA ‘ES’ELUKUM ‘ALEJHI MIN ‘EXHRIN WE MA ‘ENA MINEL-MUTEKELLIFINE
  38,87,‘IN HUWE ‘ILLA DHIKRUN LIL’ALEMINE
  38,88,WE LETA’LEMUNNE NEBE’EHU BA’DE HININ
  39,1,TENZILUL-KITABI MINEL-LAHIL-’AZIZIL-HEKIMI
  39,2,‘INNA ‘ENZELNA ‘ILEJKEL-KITABE BIL-HEKKI FA’BUDI ELLAHE MUHLISÆN LEHU ED-DINE
  39,3,‘ELA LILLAHI ED-DINUL-HALISU WEL-LEDHINE ETTEHADHU MIN DUNIHI ‘EWLIJA’E MA NA’BUDUHUM ‘ILLA LIJUKARRIBUNA ‘ILA ELLAHI ZULFA ‘INNALL-LLAHE JEHKUMU BEJNEHUM FI MA HUM FIHI JEHTELIFUNE ‘INNALL-LLAHE LA JEHDI MEN HUWE KADHIBUN KEFFARUN
  39,4,LEW ‘ERADEL-LAHU ‘EN JETTEHIDHE WELEDÆN LASTEFA MIMMA JEHLUKU MA JESHA’U SUBHANEHU HUWEL-LAHUL-WAHIDUL-KAHHARU
  39,5,HALEKA ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDE BIL-HEKKI JUKEWWIRUL-LEJLE ‘ALA EN-NEHARI WE JUKEWWIRU EN-NEHARE ‘ALEL-LEJLI WE SEHHARE ESH-SHEMSE WEL-KAMERE KULLUN JEXHRI LI’XHELIN MUSEMMEN ‘ELA HUWEL-’AZIZUL-GAFFARU
  39,6,HALEKAKUM MIN NEFSIN WAHIDETIN THUMME XHE’ALE MINHA ZEWXHEHA WE ‘ENZELE LEKUM MINEL-’EN’AM THEMANIJETE ‘EZWAXHIN JEHLUKUKUM FI BUTUNI ‘UMMEHATIKUM HALKÆN MIN BA’DI HALKIN FI DHULUMATIN THELATHIN DHELIKUMU ELLAHU REBBUKUM LEHUL-MULKU LA ‘ILAHE ‘ILLA HUWE F
  39,7,‘IN TEKFURU FE’INNALL-LLAHE GANIJUN ‘ANKUM WE LA JERDA LI’IBADIHIL-KUFRE WE ‘IN TESHKURU JERDEHU LEKUM WE LA TEZIRU WAZIRETUN WIZRE ‘UHRA THUMME ‘ILA RABBIKUM MERXHI’UKUM FEJUNEBBI’UKUM BIMA KUNTUM TA’MELUNE ‘INNEHU ‘ALIMUN BIDHATI ES-SUDURI
  39,8,WE ‘IDHA MESSEL-’INSANE DURRUN DA’A REBBEHU MUNIBÆN ‘ILEJHI THUMME ‘IDHA HAWWELEHU NI’METEN MINHU NESIJE MA KANE JED’U ‘ILEJHI MIN KABLU WE XHE’ALE LILLAHI ‘ENDADÆN LIJUDILLE ‘AN SEBILIHI KUL TEMETTA’ BIKUFRIKE KALILÆN ‘INNEKE MIN ‘ESHABI EN-NARI
  39,9,‘EMMEN HUWE KANITUN ‘ANA’EL-LEJLI SAXHIDÆN WE KA’IMÆN JEHDHERUL-’AHIRETE WE JERXHU REHMETE RABBIHI KUL HEL JESTEWIL-LEDHINE JA’LEMUNE WEL-LEDHINE LA JA’LEMUNE ‘INNEMA JETEDHEKKERU ‘ULUL-’ELBABI
  39,10,KUL JA ‘IBADIL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU ETTEKU REBBEKUM LILLEDHINE ‘EHSENU FI HEDHIHI ED-DUNJA HESENETUN WE ‘ERDU ELLAHI WASI’ATUN ‘INNEMA JUWEFFA ES-SABIRUNE ‘EXHREHUM BIGAJRI HISABIN
  39,11,KUL ‘INNI ‘UMIRTU ‘EN ‘A’BUDEL-LAHE MUHLISÆN LEHU ED-DINE
  39,12,WE ‘UMIRTU LI’N ‘EKUNE ‘EWWELEL-MUSLIMINE
  39,13,KUL ‘INNI ‘EHAFU ‘IN ‘ASEJTU RABBI ‘ADHABE JEWMIN ‘ADHIMIN
  39,14,KULI ELLAHE ‘A’BUDU MUHLISÆN LEHU DINI
  39,15,FA’BUDU MA SHI’TUM MIN DUNIHI KUL ‘INNEL-HASIRINEL-LEDHINE HASIRU ‘ENFUSEHUM WE ‘EHLIHIM JEWMEL-KIJAMETI ‘ELA DHALIKE HUWEL-HUSRANUL-MUBINU
  39,16,LEHUM MIN FEWKIHIM DHULELUN MINE EN-NARI WE MIN TEHTIHIM DHULELUN DHALIKE JUHAWWIFU ELLAHU BIHI ‘IBADEHU JA ‘IBADI FE ETTEKUNI
  39,17,WEL-LEDHINE EXHTENEBUT-TAGUTE ‘EN JA’BUDUHA WE ‘ENABU ‘ILA ELLAHI LEHUMUL-BUSHRA FEBESHSHIR ‘IBADI
  39,18,EL-LEDHINE JESTEMI’UNEL-KAWLE FEJETTEBI’UNE ‘EHSENEHU ‘ULA’IKEL-LEDHINE HEDAHUMU ELLAHU WE ‘ULA’IKE HUM ‘ULUL-’ELBABI
  39,19,‘EFEMEN HEKKA ‘ALEJHI KELIMETUL-’ADHABI ‘EFE’ENTE TUNKIDHU MEN FI EN-NARI
  39,20,LEKINIL-LEDHINE ETTEKAW REBBEHUM LEHUM GUREFUN MIN FEWKIHA GUREFUN MEBNIJETUN TEXHRI MIN TEHTIHAL-’ENHARU WA’DEL-LAHI LA JUHLIFU ELLAHUL-MI’AD
  39,21,‘ELEM TERA ‘ENNEL-LAHE ‘ENZELE MINE ES-SEMA’I MA’EN FESELEKEHU JENABI’A FIL-’ERDI THUMME JUHRIXHU BIHI ZER’ÆN MUHTELIFÆN ‘ELWANUHU THUMME JEHIXHU FETERAHU MUSFERRÆN THUMME JEXH’ALUHU HUTAMÆN ‘INNE FI DHALIKE LEDHIKRA LI’WLIL-’ELBABI
  39,22,‘EFEMEN SHEREHEL-LAHU SEDREHU LIL’ISLAMI FEHUWE ‘ALA NURIN MIN RABBIHI FEWEJLUN LILKASIJETI KULUBUHUM MIN DHIKRI ELLAHI ‘ULA’IKE FI DELALIN MUBININ
  39,23,ELLAHU NEZZELE ‘EHSENEL-HEDITHI KITABÆN MUTESHABIHÆN METHANIJE TEKSHA’IRRU MINHU XHULUDUL-LEDHINE JEHSHEWNE REBBEHUM THUMME TELINU XHULUDUHUM WE KULUBUHUM ‘ILA DHIKRI ELLAHI DHALIKE HUDA ELLAHI JEHDI BIHI MEN JESHA’U WE MEN JUDLILI ELLAHU FEMA LEHU MIN HA
  39,24,‘EFEMEN JETTEKI BIWEXHHIHI SU’EL-’ADHABI JEWMEL-KIJAMETI WE KILE LILDHDHALIMINE DHUKU MA KUNTUM TEKSIBUNE
  39,25,KEDHDHEBEL-LEDHINE MIN KABLIHIM FE’ETAHUMUL-’ADHABU MIN HEJTHU LA JESH’URUNE
  39,26,FE’EDHAKAHUMU ELLAHUL-HIZJE FIL-HEJÆTI ED-DUNJA WE LE’ADHABUL-’AHIRETI ‘EKBERU LEW KANU JA’LEMUNE
  39,27,WE LEKAD DEREBNA LILNNASI FI HADHAL-KUR’ANI MIN KULLI METHELIN LE’ALLEHUM JETEDHEKKERUNE
  39,28,KUR’ANÆN ‘AREBIJÆN GAJRE DHI ‘IWEXHIN LE’ALLEHUM JETTEKUNE
  39,29,DEREBEL-LAHU METHELÆN REXHULÆN FIHI SHUREKA’U MUTESHAKISUNE WE REXHULÆN SELEMÆN LIREXHULIN HEL JESTEWIJANI METHELÆNL-HEMDU LILLAHI BEL ‘EKTHERUHUM LA JA’LEMUNE
  39,30,‘INNEKE MEJJITUN WE ‘INNEHUM MEJJITUNE
  39,31,THUMME ‘INNEKUM JEWMEL-KIJAMETI ‘INDE RABBIKUM TEHTESIMUNE
  39,32,FEMEN ‘EDHLEMU MIMMEN KEDHEBE ‘ALA ELLAHI WE KEDHDHEBE BIS-SIDKI ‘IDH XHA’EHU ‘ELEJSE FI XHEHENNEME METHWEN LILKAFIRINE
  39,33,WEL-LEDHI XHA’E BIS-SIDKI WE SEDDEKA BIHI ‘ULA’IKE HUMUL-MUTTEKUNE
  39,34,LEHUM MA JESHA’UNE ‘INDE RABBIHIM DHALIKE XHEZA’UL-MUHSININE
  39,35,LIJUKEFFIREL-LAHU ‘ANHUM ‘ESWE’EL-LEDHI ‘AMILU WE JEXHZIJEHUM ‘EXHREHUM BI’EHSENIL-LEDHI KANU JA’MELUNE
  39,36,‘ELEJSEL-LAHU BIKAFIN ‘ABDEHU WE JUHAWWIFUNEKE BIEL-LEDHINE MIN DUNIHI WE MEN JUDLILI ELLAHU FEMA LEHU MIN HADIN
  39,37,WE MEN JEHDI ELLAHU FEMA LEHU MIN MUDILLIN ‘ELEJSEL-LAHU BI’AZIZIN DHI ENTIKAMIN
  39,38,WE LE’IN SE’ELTEHUM MEN HALEKA ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDE LEJEKULUNNEL-LAHU KUL ‘EFERE’EJTUM MA TED’UNE MIN DUNI ELLAHI ‘IN ‘ERADENIJEL-LAHU BIDURRIN HEL HUNNE KASHIFATU DURRIHI ‘EW ‘ERADENI BIREHMETIN HEL HUNNE MUMSIKATU REHMETIHI KUL HESBIJEL-LAHU ‘ALEJHI JE
  39,39,KUL JA KAWMI A’MELU ‘ALA MEKANETIKUM ‘INNI ‘AMILUN FESEWFE TA’LEMUNE
  39,40,MEN JE’TIHI ‘ADHABUN JUHZIHI WE JEHILLU ‘ALEJHI ‘ADHABUN MUKIMUN
  39,41,‘INNA ‘ENZELNA ‘ALEJKEL-KITABE LILNNASI BIL-HEKKI FEMENI EHTEDA FELINEFSIHI WE MEN DELLE FE’INNEMA JEDILLU ‘ALEJHA WE MA ‘ENTE ‘ALEJHIM BIWEKILIN
  39,42,ELLAHU JETEWEFFAL-’ENFUSE HINE MEWTIHA WE E-ETI LEM TEMUT FI MENAMIHA FEJUMSIKU ELLETI KADA ‘ALEJHAL-MEWTE WE JURSILUL-’UHRA ‘ILA ‘EXHELIN MUSEMMEN ‘INNE FI DHALIKE LE’AJATIN LIKAWMIN JETEFEKKERUNE
  39,43,‘EMI ETTEHADHU MIN DUNI ELLAHI SHUFA’A’E KUL ‘EWELEW KANU LA JEMLIKUNE SHEJ’ÆN WE LA JA’KILUNE
  39,44,KUL LILLAHI ESH-SHEFA’ATU XHEMI’ÆN LEHU MULKU ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI THUMME ‘ILEJHI TURXHA’UNE
  39,45,WE ‘IDHA DHUKIREL-LAHU WEHDEHU ESHME’EZZET KULUBUL-LEDHINE LA JU’UMINUNE BIL-’AHIRETI WE ‘IDHA DHUKIREL-LEDHINE MIN DUNIHI ‘IDHA HUM JESTEBSHIRUNE
  39,46,KULIL-LEHUMME FATIRE ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI ‘ALIMEL-GAJBI WE ESH-SHEHADETI ‘ENTE TEHKUMU BEJNE ‘IBADIKE FI MA KANU FIHI JEHTELIFUNE
  39,47,WE LEW ‘ENNE LILLEDHINE DHELEMU MA FIL-’ERDI XHEMI’ÆN WE MITHLEHU ME’AHU LAFTEDEW BIHI MIN SU’IL-’ADHABI JEWMEL-KIJAMETI WE BEDA LEHUM MINEL-LAHI MA LEM JEKUNU JEHTESIBUNE
  39,48,WE BEDA LEHUM SEJJI’ATU MA KESEBU WE HAKA BIHIM MA KANU BIHI JESTEHZI’UN
  39,49,FE’IDHA MESSEL-’INSANE DURRUN DA’ANA THUMME ‘IDHA HAWWELNAHU NI’METEN MINNA KALE ‘INNEMA ‘UTITUHU ‘ALA ‘ILMIN BEL HIJE FITNETUN WE LEKINNE ‘EKTHEREHUM LA JA’LEMUNE
  39,50,KAD KALEHAL-LEDHINE MIN KABLIHIM FEMA ‘EGNA ‘ANHUM MA KANU JEKSIBUNE
  39,51,FE’ESABEHUM SEJJI’ATU MA KESEBU WEL-LEDHINE DHELEMU MIN HA’UULA’ SEJUSIBUHUM SEJJI’ATU MA KESEBU WE MA HUM BIMU’XHIZINE
  39,52,‘EWELEM JA’LEMU ‘ENNEL-LAHE JEBSUTU ER-RIZKA LIMEN JESHA’U WE JEKDIRU ‘INNE FI DHALIKE LE’AJATIN LIKAWMIN JU’UMINUNE
  39,53,KUL JA ‘IBADIL-LEDHINE ‘ESREFU ‘ALA ‘ENFUSIHIM LA TEKNETU MIN REHMETI ELLAHI ‘INNALL-LLAHE JEGFIRU EDH-DHUNUBE XHEMI’ÆN ‘INNEHU HUWEL-GAFURU ER-REHIMU
  39,54,WE ‘ENIBU ‘ILA RABBIKUM WE ‘ESLIMU LEHU MIN KABLI ‘EN JE’TIJEKUMUL-’ADHABU THUMME LA TUNSERUNE
  39,55,WE ETTEBI’U ‘EHSENE MA ‘UNZILE ‘ILEJKUM MIN RABBIKUM MIN KABLI ‘EN JE’TIJEKUMUL-’ADHABU BEGTETEN WE ‘ENTUM LA TESH’URUNE
  39,56,‘EN TEKULE NEFSUN JA HESRETA ‘ALA MA FERRETTU FI XHENBI ELLAHI WE ‘IN KUNTU LEMINE ES-SAHIRINE
  39,57,‘EW TEKULE LEW ‘ENNEL-LAHE HEDANI LEKUNTU MINEL-MUTTEKINE
  39,58,‘EW TEKULE HINE TERAL-’ADHABE LEW ‘ENNE LI KERRETEN FE’EKUNE MINEL-MUHSININE
  39,59,BELA KAD XHA’ETKE ‘AJATI FEKEDHDHEBTE BIHA WE ESTEKBERTE WE KUNTE MINEL-KAFIRINE
  39,60,WE JEWMEL-KIJAMETI TERAL-LEDHINE KEDHEBU ‘ALA ELLAHI WUXHUHUHUM MUSWEDDETUN ‘ELEJSE FI XHEHENNEME METHWEN LILMUTEKEBBIRINE
  39,61,WE JUNEXHXHI ELLAHUL-LEDHINE ETTEKAW BIMEFAZETIHIM LA JEMESSUHUMU ES-SU’U WE LA HUM JEHZENUNE
  39,62,ELLAHU HALIKU KULLI SHEJ’IN WE HUWE ‘ALA KULLI SHEJ’IN WE KILUN
  39,63,LEHU MEKALIDU ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI WEL-LEDHINE KEFERU BI’AJATI ELLAHI ‘ULA’IKE HUMUL-HASIRUNE
  39,64,KUL ‘EFEGAJREL-LAHI TE’MURUNNI ‘A’BUDU ‘EJJUHAL-XHAHILUNE
  39,65,WE LEKAD ‘UHIJE ‘ILEJKE WE ‘ILAL-LEDHINE MIN KABLIKE LE’IN ‘ESHREKTE LEJEHBETENNE ‘AMELUKE WE LETEKUNENNE MINEL-HASIRINE
  39,66,BELI ELLAHE FA’BUD WE KUN MINE ESH-SHAKIRINE
  39,67,WE MA KADERU ELLAHE HEKKA KADRIHI WEL-’ERDU XHEMI’ÆN KABDETUHU JEWMEL-KIJAMETI WE ES-SEMAWATU METWIJATUN BIJEMINIHI SUBHANEHU WE TA’ALA ‘AMMA JUSHRIKUNE
  39,68,WE NUFIHA FI ES-SURI FESA’IKA MEN FI ES-SEMAWATI WE MEN FIL-’ERDI ‘ILLA MEN SHA’EL-LAHU THUMME NUFIHA FIHI ‘UHRA FE’IDHA HUM KIJAMUN JENDHURUNE
  39,69,WE ‘ESHREKATIL-’ERDU BINURI RABBIHA WE WUDI’AL-KITABU WE XHI’E BIN-NEBIJINE WE ESH-SHUHEDA’I WE KUDIJE BEJNEHUM BIL-HEKKI WE HUM LA JUDHLEMUNE
  39,70,WE WUFFIJET KULLU NEFSIN MA ‘AMILET WE HUWE ‘A’LEMU BIMA JEF’ALUNE
  39,71,WE SIKAL-LEDHINE KEFERU ‘ILA XHEHENNEME ZUMERÆN HETTA ‘IDHA XHA’UHA FUTIHET ‘EBWABUHA WE KALE LEHUM HAZENETUHA ‘ELEM JE’TIKUM RUSULUN MINKUM JETLUNE ‘ALEJKUM ‘AJATI RABBIKUM WE JUNDHIRUNEKUM LIKA’E JEWMIKUM HADHA KALU BELA WE LEKIN HEKKAT KELIMETUL-’ADHAB
  39,72,KILE EDHULU ‘EBWABE XHEHENNEME HALIDINE FIHA FEBI’SE METHWAL-MUTEKEBBIRINE
  39,73,WE SIKAL-LEDHINE ETTEKAW REBBEHUM ‘ILAL-XHENNETI ZUMERÆN HETTA ‘IDHA XHA’UHA WE FUTIHET ‘EBWABUHA WE KALE LEHUM HAZENETUHA SELAMUN ‘ALEJKUM TIBTUM FADHULUHA HALIDINE
  39,74,WE KALUL-HEMDU LILLAHIL-LEDHI SEDEKANA WA’DEHU WE ‘EWRETHENAL-’ERDE NETEBEWWE’U MINEL-XHENNETI HEJTHU NESHA’U FENI’ME ‘EXHRUL-’AMILINE
  39,75,WE TERAL-MELA’IKETE HAFFINE MIN HEWLIL-’ARSHI JUSEBBIHUNE BIHEMDI RABBIHIM WE KUDIJE BEJNEHUM BIL-HEKKI WE KILEL-HEMDU LILLAHI RABBIL-’ALEMINE
  40,1,HA-MIM
  40,2,TENZILUL-KITABI MINEL-LAHIL-’AZIZIL-’ALIMI
  40,3,GAFIRI EDH-DHENBI WE KABILIT-TEWBI SHEDIDIL-’IKABI DHIT-TEWLI LA ‘ILAHE ‘ILLA HUWE ‘ILEJHIL-MESIRU
  40,4,MA JUXHADILU FI ‘AJATI ELLAHI ‘ILLAL-LEDHINE KEFERU FELA JEGRURKE TEKALLUBUHUM FIL-BILADI
  40,5,KEDHDHEBET KABLEHUM KAWMU NUHIN WEL-’EHZABU MIN BA’DIHIM WE HEMMET KULLU ‘UMMETIN BIRESULIHIM LIJE’HUDHUHU WE XHADELU BIL-BATILI LIJUDHIDU BIHIL-HEKKA FE’EHADHTUHUM FEKEJFE KANE ‘IKABI
  40,6,WE KEDHELIKE HEKKAT KELIMETU RABBIKE ‘ALEL-LEDHINE KEFERU ‘ENNEHUM ‘ESHABU EN-NARI
  40,7,EL-LEDHINE JEHMILUNEL-’ARSHE WE MEN HEWLEHU JUSEBBIHUNE BIHEMDI RABBIHIM WE JU’UMINUNE BIHI WE JESTEGFIRUNE LILLEDHINE ‘AMENU REBBENA WESI’TE KULLE SHEJ’IN REHMETEN WE ‘ILMÆN FAGFIR LILLEDHINE TABU WE ETTEBA’U SEBILEKE WE KIHIM ‘ADHABEL-XHEHIMI
  40,8,REBBENA WE ‘EDHILHUM XHENNATI ‘ADNIN ELLETI WE’ADTEHUM WE MEN SELEHE MIN ‘ABA’IHIM WE ‘EZWAXHIHIM WE DHURRIJATIHIM ‘INNEKE ‘ENTEL-’AZIZUL-HEKIMU
  40,9,WE KIHIMU ES-SEJJI’ATI WE MEN TEKI ES-SEJJI’ATI JEWME’IDHIN FEKAD REHIMTEHU WE DHELIKE HUWEL-FEWZUL-’ADHIMU
  40,10,‘INNEL-LEDHINE KEFERU JUNADEWNE LEMEKTU ELLAHI ‘EKBERU MIN MEKTIKUM ‘ENFUSEKUM ‘IDH TUD’AWNE ‘ILAL-’IMANI FETEKFURUNE
  40,11,KALU REBBENA ‘EMETTENA ETHNETEJNI WE ‘EHJEJTENA ETHNETEJNI FA’TEREFNA BIDHUNUBINA FEHEL ‘ILA HURUXHIN MIN SEBILIN
  40,12,DHALIKUM BI’ENNEHU ‘IDHA DU’IJEL-LAHU WEHDEHU KEFERTUM WE ‘IN JUSHREK BIHI TU’UMINU FALHUKMU LILLAHIL-’ALIJIL-KEBIRI
  40,13,HUWEL-LEDHI JURIKUM ‘AJATIHI WE JUNEZZILU LEKUM MINE ES-SEMA’I RIZKÆN WE MA JETEDHEKKERU ‘ILLA MEN JUNIBU
  40,14,FAD’U ELLAHE MUHLISINE LEHU ED-DINE WE LEW KERIHEL-KAFIRUNE
  40,15,REFI’U ED-DEREXHATI DHUL-’ARSHI JULKI ER-RUHE MIN ‘EMRIHI ‘ALA MEN JESHA’U MIN ‘IBADIHI LIJUNDHIRE JEWMET-TELAKI
  40,16,JEWME HUM BARIZUNE LA JEHFA ‘ALA ELLAHI MINHUM SHEJ’UN LIMENIL-MULKUL-JEWME LILLAHIL-WAHIDIL-KAHHARI
  40,17,EL-JEWME TUXHZA KULLU NEFSIN BIMA KESEBET LA DHULMEL-JEWME ‘INNALL-LLAHE SERI’UL-HISABI
  40,18,WE ‘ENDHIRHUM JEWMEL-’AZIFETI ‘IDHIL-KULUBU LEDAL-HENAXHIRI KADHIMINE MA LILDHDHALIMINE MIN HEMIMIN WE LA SHEFI’IN JUTA’U
  40,19,JA’LEMU HA’INETEL-’A’JUNI WE MA TUHFI ES-SUDURU
  40,20,WEL-LAHU JEKDI BIL-HEKKI WEL-LEDHINE JED’UNE MIN DUNIHI LA JEKDUNE BISHEJ’IN ‘INNALL-LLAHE HUWE ES-SEMI’UL-BESIRU
  40,21,‘EWE LEM JESIRU FIL-’ERDI FEJENDHURU KEJFE KANE ‘AKIBETUL-LEDHINE KANU MIN KABLIHIM KANU HUM ‘ESHEDDE MINHUM KUWETEN WE ‘ATHARÆN FIL-’ERDI FE’EHADHEHUMU ELLAHU BIDHUNUBIHIM WE MA KANE LEHUM MINI ELLAHI MIN WAKIN
  40,22,DHALIKE BI’ENNEHUM KANET TE’TIHIM RUSULUHUM BIL-BEJJINATI FEKEFERU FE’EHADHEHUMU ELLAHU ‘INNEHU KAWIJUN SHEDIDUL-’IKABI
  40,23,WE LEKAD ‘ERSELNA MUSA BI’AJATINA WE SULTANIN MUBININ
  40,24,‘ILA FIR’AWNE WE HAMANE WE KARUNE FEKALU SAHIRUN KEDHDHABUN
  40,25,FELEMMA XHA’EHUM BIL-HEKKI MIN ‘INDINA KALU EKTULU ‘EBNA’EL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU ME’AHU WE ESTEHJU NISA’EHUM WE MA KEJDUL-KAFIRINE ‘ILLA FI DELALIN
  40,26,WE KALE FIR’AWNU DHERUNI ‘EKTUL MUSA WE LIED’U REBBEHU ‘INNI ‘EHAFU ‘EN JUBEDDILE DINEKUM ‘EW ‘EN JUDHHIRE FIL-’ERDIL-FESADE
  40,27,WE KALE MUSA ‘INNI ‘UDHTU BIREBBI WE RABBIKUM MIN KULLI MUTEKEBBIRIN LA JU’UMINU BIJEWMIL-HISABI
  40,28,WE KALE REXHULUN MU’UMINUN MIN ‘ALI FIR’AWNE JEKTUMU ‘IMANEHU ‘ETEKTULUNE REXHULÆN ‘EN JEKULE RABBIJEL-LAHU WE KAD XHA’EKUM BIL-BEJJINATI MIN RABBIKUM WE ‘IN JEKU KADHIBÆN FE’ALEJHI KEDHIBUHU WE ‘IN JEKU SADIKÆN JUSIBKUM BA’DUL-LEDHI JA’IDUKUM ‘INNALL-LLA
  40,29,JA KAWMI LEKUMUL-MULKUL-JEWME DHAHIRINE FIL-’ERDI FEMEN JENSURUNA MIN BE’SI ELLAHI ‘IN XHA’ENA KALE FIR’AWNU MA ‘URIKUM ‘ILLA MA ‘ERA WE MA ‘EHDIKUM ‘ILLA SEBILE ER-RESHADI
  40,30,WE KALEL-LEDHI ‘AMENE JA KAWMI ‘INNI ‘EHAFU ‘ALEJKUM MITHLE JEWMIL-’EHZABI
  40,31,MITHLE DE’BI KAWMI NUHIN WE ‘ADIN WE THEMUDE WEL-LEDHINE MIN BA’DIHIM WE MALLAHU JURIDU DHULMÆN LIL’IBADI
  40,32,WE JAKAWMI ‘INNI ‘EHAFU ‘ALEJKUM JEWMET-TENADI
  40,33,JEWME TUWELLUNE MUDBIRINE MA LEKUM MINEL-LAHI MIN ‘ASIMIN WE MEN JUDLILI ELLAHU FEMA LEHU MIN HADIN
  40,34,WE LEKAD XHA’EKUM JUSUFU MIN KABLU BIL-BEJJINATI FEMA ZILTUM FI SHEKKIN MIMMA XHA’EKUM BIHI HETTA ‘IDHA HELEKE KULTUM LEN JEB’ATHEL-LAHU MIN BA’DIHI RESULÆN KEDHALIKE JUDILLU ELLAHU MEN HUWE MUSRIFUN MURTABUN
  40,35,EL-LEDHINE JUXHADILUNE FI ‘AJATI ELLAHI BIGAJRI SULTANIN ‘ETAHUM KEBURE MEKTÆN ‘INDEL-LAHI WE ‘INDEL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU KEDHALIKE JETBA’U ELLAHU ‘ALA KULLI KALBI MUTEKEBBIRIN XHEBBARIN
  40,36,WE KALE FIR’AWNU JA HAMANU EBNI LI SERHÆN LE’ALLI ‘EBLUGUL-’ESBABE
  40,37,‘ESBABE ES-SEMAWATI FE’ETTELI’A ‘ILA ‘ILEHI MUSA WE ‘INNI LE’EDHUNNUHU KADHIBÆN WE KEDHELIKE ZUJJINE LIFIR’AWNE SU’U ‘AMELIHI WE SUDDE ‘ANI ES-SEBILI WE MA KEJDU FIR’AWNE ‘ILLA FI TEBABIN
  40,38,WE KALEL-LEDHI ‘AMENE JA KAWMI ETTEBI’UNI ‘EHDIKUM SEBILE ER-RESHADI
  40,39,JA KAWMI ‘INNEMA HEDHIHIL-HEJA ETU ED-DUNJA META’UN WE ‘INNEL-’AHIRETE HIJE DARUL-KARARI
  40,40,MEN ‘AMILE SEJJI’ETEN FELA JUXHZA ‘ILLA MITHLEHA WE MEN ‘AMILE SALIHÆN MIN DHEKERIN ‘EW ‘UNTHA WE HUWE MU’UMINUN FE’ULA’IKE JEDHULUNEL-XHENNETE JURZEKUNE FIHA BIGAJRI HISABIN
  40,41,WE JAKAWMI MA LI ‘ED’UKUM ‘ILA EN-NEXHÆTI WE TED’UNENI ‘ILA EN-NARI
  40,42,TED’UNENI LI’KFURE BILLAHI WE ‘USHRIKE BIHI MA LEJSE LI BIHI ‘ILMUN WE ‘ENA ‘ED’UKUM ‘ILAL-’AZIZIL-GAFFARI
  40,43,LA XHEREME ‘ENNEMA TED’UNENI ‘ILEJHI LEJSE LEHU DA’WETUN FI ED-DUNJA WE LA FIL-’AHIRETI WE ‘ENNE MEREDDENA ‘ILA ELLAHI WE ‘ENNEL-MUSRIFINE HUM ‘ESHABU EN-NARI
  40,44,FESETEDHKURUNE MA ‘EKULU LEKUM WE ‘UFEWWIDU ‘EMRI ‘ILA ELLAHI ‘INNALL-LLAHE BESIRUN BIL-’IBADI
  40,45,FEWEKAHU ELLAHU SEJJI’ATI MA MEKERU WE HAKA BI’ALI FIR’AWNE SU’UL-’ADHABI
  40,46,EN-NARU JU’REDUNE ‘ALEJHA GUDUWÆN WE ‘ASHIJÆN WE JEWME TEKUMU ES-SA’ATU ‘EDHILU ‘ALE FIR’AWNE ‘ESHEDDEL-’ADHABI
  40,47,WE ‘IDH JETEHAXHXHUNE FI EN-NARI FEJEKULU ED-DU’AFA’U LILLEDHINE ESTEKBERU ‘INNA KUNNA LEKUM TEBA’ÆN FEHEL ‘ENTUM MUGNUNE ‘ANNA NESIBÆN MINE EN-NARI
  40,48,KALEL-LEDHINE ESTEKBERU ‘INNA KULLUN FIHA ‘INNALL-LLAHE KAD HEKEME BEJNEL-’IBADI
  40,49,WE KALEL-LEDHINE FI EN-NARI LIHAZENETI XHEHENNEME ED’U REBBEKUM JUHAFFIF ‘ANNA JEWMÆN MINEL-’ADHABI
  40,50,KALU ‘EWE LEM TEKU TE’TIKUM RUSULUKUM BIL-BEJJINATI KALU BELA KALU FAD’U WE MA DU’A’UL-KAFIRINE ‘ILLA FI DELALIN
  40,51,‘INNA LENENSURU RUSULENA WEL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU FIL-HEJÆTI ED-DUNJA WE JEWME JEKUMUL-’ESH/HADU
  40,52,JEWME LA JENFA’U EDH-DHALIMINE MA’DHIRETUHUM WE LEHUMUL-LA’NETU WE LEHUM SU’U ED-DARI
  40,53,WE LEKAD ‘ATEJNA MUSAL-HUDA WE ‘EWRETHNA BENI ‘ISRA’ILEL-KITABE
  40,54,HUDEN WE DHIKRA LI’WLIL-’ELBABI
  40,55,FASBIR ‘INNE WA’DEL-LAHI HEKKUN WE ESTEGFIR LIDHENBIKE WE SEBBIH BIHEMDI RABBIKE BIL-’ASHIJI WEL-’IBKARI
  40,56,‘INNEL-LEDHINE JUXHADILUNE FI ‘AJATI ELLAHI BIGAJRI SULTANIN ‘ETAHUM ‘IN FI SUDURIHIM ‘ILLA KIBRUN MA HUM BIBALIGIHI FASTA’IDH BILLAHI ‘INNEHU HUWE ES-SEMI’UL-BESIRU
  40,57,LEHALKU ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI ‘EKBERU MIN HALKI EN-NASI WE LEKINNE ‘EKTHERE EN-NASI LA JA’LEMUNE
  40,58,WE MA JESTEWIL-’A’MA WEL-BESIRU WEL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU WE ‘AMILU ES-SALIHATI WE LAL-MUSI’U KALILÆN MA TETEDHEKKERUNE
  40,59,‘INNE ES-SA’ATE LE’ATIJETUN LA REJBE FIHA WE LEKINNE ‘EKTHERE EN-NASI LA JU’UMINUNE
  40,60,WE KALE REBBUKUM ED’UNI ‘ESTEXHIB LEKUM ‘INNEL-LEDHINE JESTEKBIRUNE ‘AN ‘IBADETI SEJEDHULUNE XHEHENNEME DAHIRINE
  40,61,ELLAHUL-LEDHI XHE’ALE LEKUMUL-LEJLE LITESKUNU FIHI WE EN-NEHARE MUBSIRÆN ‘INNALL-LLAHE LEDHU FEDLIN ‘ALA EN-NASI WE LEKINNE ‘EKTHERE EN-NASI LA JESHKURUNE
  40,62,DHELIKUMU ELLAHU REBBUKUM HALIKU KULLI SHEJ’IN LA ‘ILAHE ‘ILLA HUWE FE’ENNA TU’UFEKUNE
  40,63,KEDHALIKE JU’UFEKUL-LEDHINE KANU BI’AJATI ELLAHI JEXHHEDUNE
  40,64,ELLAHUL-LEDHI XHE’ALE LEKUMUL-’ERDE KARARÆN WE ES-SEMA’E BINA’EN WE SEWWEREKUM FE’EHSENE SUWEREKUM WE REZEKAKUM MINET-TEJJIBATI DHELIKUMU ELLAHU REBBUKUM FETEBAREKEL-LAHU REBBUL-’ALEMINE
  40,65,HUWEL-HEJJU LA ‘ILAHE ‘ILLA HUWE FAD’UHU MUHLISINE LEHU ED-DINEL-HEMDU LILLAHI RABBIL-’ALEMINE
  40,66,KUL ‘INNI NUHITU ‘EN ‘A’BUDEL-LEDHINE TED’UNE MIN DUNI ELLAHI LEMMA XHA’ENIJEL-BEJJINATU MIN RABBI WE ‘UMIRTU ‘EN ‘USLIME LIREBBIL-’ALEMINE
  40,67,HUWEL-LEDHI HALEKAKUM MIN TURABIN THUMME MIN NUTFETIN THUMME MIN ‘ALEKATIN THUMME JUHRIXHUKUM TIFLÆN THUMME LITEBLUGU ‘ESHUDDEKUM THUMME LITEKUNU SHUJUHÆN WE MINKUM MEN JUTEWEFFA MIN KABLU WE LITEBLUGU ‘EXHELÆN MUSEMMEN WE LE’ALLEKUM TA’KILUNE
  40,68,HUWEL-LEDHI JUHJI WE JUMITU FE’IDHA KADA ‘EMRÆN FE’INNEMA JEKULU LEHU KUN FEJEKUNU
  40,69,‘ELEM TERA ‘ILAL-LEDHINE JUXHADILUNE FI ‘AJATI ELLAHI ‘ENNA JUSREFUNE
  40,70,EL-LEDHINE KEDHDHEBU BIL-KITABI WE BIMA ‘ERSELNA BIHI RUSULENA FESEWFE JA’LEMUNE
  40,71,‘IDHIL-’EGLALU FI ‘A’NAKIHIM WE ES-SELASILU JUSHEBUNE
  40,72,FIL-HEMIMI THUMME FI EN-NARI JUSXHERUNE
  40,73,THUMME KILE LEHUM ‘EJNE MA KUNTUM TUSHRIKUNE
  40,74,MIN DUNI ELLAHI KALU DELLU ‘ANNA BEL LEM NEKUN NED’U MIN KABLU SHEJ’ÆN KEDHALIKE JUDILLU ELLAHUL-KAFIRINE
  40,75,DHALIKUM BIMA KUNTUM TEFREHUNE FIL-’ERDI BIGAJRIL-HEKKI WE BIMA KUNTUM TEMREHUNE
  40,76,EDHULU ‘EBWABE XHEHENNEME HALIDINE FIHA FEBI’SE METHWAL-MUTEKEBBIRINE
  40,77,FASBIR ‘INNE WA’DEL-LAHI HEKKUN FE’IMMA NURIJENNEKE BA’DEL-LEDHI NA’IDUHUM ‘EW NETEWEFFEJENNEKE FE’ILEJNA JURXHA’UNE
  40,78,WE LEKAD ‘ERSELNA RUSULÆN MIN KABLIKE MINHUM MEN KASESNA ‘ALEJKE WE MINHUM MEN LEM NEKSUS ‘ALEJKE WE MA KANE LIRESULIN ‘EN JE’TIJE BI’AJETIN ‘ILLA BI’IDHNI ELLAHI FE’IDHA XHA’E ‘EMRU ELLAHI KUDIJE BIL-HEKKI WE HASIRE HUNALIKEL-MUBTILUNE
  40,79,ELLAHUL-LEDHI XHE’ALE LEKUMUL-’EN’AM LITERKEBU MINHA WE MINHA TE’KULUNE
  40,80,WE LEKUM FIHA MENAFI’U WE LITEBLUGU ‘ALEJHA HAXHETEN FI SUDURIKUM WE ‘ALEJHA WE ‘ALEL-FULKI TUHMELUNE
  40,81,WE JURIKUM ‘AJATIHI FE’EJJE ‘AJATI ELLAHI TUNKIRUNE
  40,82,‘EFELEM JESIRU FIL-’ERDI FEJENDHURU KEJFE KANE ‘AKIBETUL-LEDHINE MIN KABLIHIM KANU ‘EKTHERE MINHUM WE ‘ESHEDDE KUWETEN WE ‘ATHARÆN FIL-’ERDI FEMA ‘EGNA ‘ANHUM MA KANU JEKSIBUNE
  40,83,FELEMMA XHA’ET/HUM RUSULUHUM BIL-BEJJINATI FERIHU BIMA ‘INDEHUM MINEL-’ILMI WE HAKA BIHIM MA KANU BIHI JESTEHZI’UN
  40,84,FELEMMA RE’EW BE’SENA KALU ‘AMENNA BILLAHI WEHDEHU WE KEFERNA BIMA KUNNA BIHI MUSHRIKINE
  40,85,FELEM JEKU JENFA’UHUM ‘IMANUHUM LEMMA RE’EW BE’SENA SUNNETEL-LAHI ELLETI KAD HALET FI ‘IBADIHI WE HASIRE HUNALIKEL-KAFIRUNE
  41,1,HA-MIM
  41,2,TENZILUN MINE ER-REHMANI ER-REHIMI
  41,3,KITABUN FUSSILET ‘AJATUHU KUR’ANÆN ‘AREBIJÆN LIKAWMIN JA’LEMUNE
  41,4,BESHIRÆN WE NEDHIRÆN FE’A’REDE ‘EKTHERUHUM FEHUM LA JESMA’UNE
  41,5,WE KALU KULUBUNA FI ‘EKINNETIN MIMMA TED’UNA ‘ILEJHI WE FI ‘ADHANINA WEKRUN WE MIN BEJNINA WE BEJNIKE HIXHABUN FA’MEL ‘INNENA ‘AMILUNE
  41,6,KUL ‘INNEMA ‘ENA BESHERUN MITHLUKUM JUHA ‘ILEJJE ‘ENNEMA ‘ILEHUKUM ‘ILEHUN WAHIDUN FASTEKIMU ‘ILEJHI WE ESTEGFIRUHU WE WEJLUN LILMUSHRIKINE
  41,7,EL-LEDHINE LA JU’UTUNE EZ-ZEKÆTE WE HUM BIL-’AHIRETI HUM KAFIRUNE
  41,8,‘INNEL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU WE ‘AMILU ES-SALIHATI LEHUM ‘EXHRUN GAJRU MEMNUNIN
  41,9,KUL ‘E’INNEKUM LETEKFURUNE BIEL-LEDHI HALEKAL-’ERDE FI JEWMEJNI WE TEXH’ALUNE LEHU ‘ENDADÆN DHALIKE REBBUL-’ALEMINE
  41,10,WE XHE’ALE FIHA REWASIJE MIN FEWKIHA WE BAREKE FIHA WE KADDERE FIHA ‘EKWATEHA FI ‘ERBE’ATI ‘EJJAMIN SEWA’EN LILSSA’ILINE
  41,11,THUMME ESTEWA ‘ILA ES-SEMA’I WE HIJE DUHANUN FEKALE LEHA WE LIL’ERDI EI’TIJA TEW’ÆN ‘EW KERHÆN KALETA ‘ETEJNA TA’I’INE
  41,12,FEKADAHUNNE SEB’A SEMAWATIN FI JEWMEJNI WE ‘EWHA FI KULLI SEMA’IN ‘EMREHA WE ZEJJENNA ES-SEMA’E ED-DUNJA BIMESABIHE WE HIFDHÆN DHALIKE TEKDIRUL-’AZIZIL-’ALIMI
  41,13,FE’IN ‘A’REDU FEKUL ‘ENDHERTUKUM SA’IKATEN MITHLE SA’IKATI ‘ADIN WE THEMUDE
  41,14,‘IDH XHA’ET/HUMU ER-RUSULU MIN BEJNI ‘EJDIHIM WE MIN HALFIHIM ‘ELLA TA’BUDU ‘ILLALLAHE KALU LEW SHA’E REBBUNA LE’ENZELE MELA’IKETEN FE’INNA BIMA ‘URSILTUM BIHI KAFIRUNE
  41,15,FE’EMMA ‘ADUN FASTEKBERU FIL-’ERDI BIGAJRIL-HEKKI WE KALU MEN ‘ESHEDDU MINNA KUWETEN ‘EWELEM JEREW ‘ENNEL-LAHEL-LEDHI HALEKAHUM HUWE ‘ESHEDDU MINHUM KUWETEN WE KANU BI’AJATINA JEXHHEDUNE
  41,16,FE’ERSELNA ‘ALEJHIM RIHÆN SERSERÆN FI ‘EJJAMIN NEHISATIN LINUDHIKAHUM ‘ADHABEL-HIZJI FIL-HEJÆTI ED-DUNJA WE LE’ADHABUL-’AHIRETI ‘EHZA WE HUM LA JUNSERUNE
  41,17,WE ‘EMMA THEMUDU FEHEDEJNAHUM FASTEHEBBUL-’AMA ‘ALEL-HUDA FE’EHADHET/HUM SA’IKATUL-’ADHABIL-HUNI BIMA KANU JEKSIBUNE
  41,18,WE NEXHXHEJNAL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU WE KANU JETTEKUNE
  41,19,WE JEWME JUHSHERU ‘A’DA’U ELLAHI ‘ILA EN-NARI FEHUM JUZA’UNE
  41,20,HETTA ‘IDHA MA XHA’UHA SHEHIDE ‘ALEJHIM SEM’UHUM WE ‘EBSARUHUM WE XHULUDUHUM BIMA KANU JA’MELUNE
  41,21,WE KALU LIXHULUDIHIM LIME SHEHIDTUM ‘ALEJNA KALU ‘ENTEKANALLAHUL-LEDHI ‘ENTEKA KULLE SHEJ’IN WE HUWE HALEKAKUM ‘EWWELE MERRETIN WE ‘ILEJHI TURXHA’UNE
  41,22,WE MA KUNTUM TESTETIRUNE ‘EN JESH/HEDE ‘ALEJKUM SEM’UKUM WE LA ‘EBSARUKUM WE LA XHULUDUKUM WE LEKIN DHENENTUM ‘ENNEL-LAHE LA JA’LEMU KETHIRÆN MIMMA TA’MELUNE
  41,23,WE DHELIKUM DHENNUKUMUL-LEDHI DHENENTUM BIREBBIKUM ‘ERDAKUM FE’ESBEHTUM MINEL-HASIRINE
  41,24,FE’IN JESBIRU FALNNARU METHWEN LEHUM WE ‘IN JESTA’TIBU FEMA HUM MINEL-MU’TEBINE
  41,25,WE KAJJEDNA LEHUM KURENA’E FEZEJJENU LEHUM MA BEJNE ‘EJDIHIM WE MA HALFEHUM WE HEKKA ‘ALEJHIMUL-KAWLU FI ‘UMEMIN KAD HALET MIN KABLIHIM MINEL-XHINNI WEL-’INSI ‘INNEHUM KANU HASIRINE
  41,26,WE KALEL-LEDHINE KEFERU LA TESMA’U LIHEDHAL-KUR’ANI WEL-GAW FIHI LE’ALLEKUM TEGLIBUNE
  41,27,FELENUDHIKANNEL-LEDHINE KEFERU ‘ADHABÆN SHEDIDÆN WE LENEXHZIJENNEHUM ‘ESWE’EL-LEDHI KANU JA’MELUNE
  41,28,DHALIKE XHEZA’U ‘A’DA’I ELLAHI EN-NARU LEHUM FIHA DARUL-HULDI XHEZA’EN BIMA KANU BI’AJATINA JEXHHEDUNE
  41,29,WE KALEL-LEDHINE KEFERU REBBENA ‘ERINAL-LEDHEJNI ‘EDELLANA MINEL-XHINNI WEL-’INSI NEXH’ALHUMA TEHTE ‘EKDAMINA LIJEKUNA MINEL-’ESFELINE
  41,30,‘INNEL-LEDHINE KALU REBBUNALLAHU THUMME ESTEKAMU TETENEZZELU ‘ALEJHIMUL-MELA’IKETU ‘ELLA TEHAFU WE LA TEHZENU WE ‘EBSHIRU BIL-XHENNETI ELLETI KUNTUM TU’ADUNE
  41,31,NEHNU ‘EWLIJA’UUKUM FIL-HEJÆTI ED-DUNJA WE FIL-’AHIRETI WE LEKUM FIHA MA TESHTEHI ‘ENFUSUKUM WE LEKUM FIHA MA TEDDA’UNE
  41,32,NUZULÆN MIN GAFURIN REHIMIN
  41,33,WE MEN ‘EHSENU KAWLÆN MIMMEN DA’A ‘ILA ELLAHI WE ‘AMILE SALIHÆN WE KALE ‘INNENI MINEL-MUSLIMINE
  41,34,WE LA TESTEWIL-HESENETU WE LA ES-SEJJI’ETU EDFA’ BI-ETI HIJE ‘EHSENU FE’IDHAL-LEDHI BEJNEKE WE BEJNEHU ‘ADAWETUN KE’ENNEHU WE LIJUN HEMIMUN
  41,35,WE MA JULEKKAHA ‘ILLAL-LEDHINE SEBERU WE MA JULEKKAHA ‘ILLA DHU HEDHDHIN ‘ADHIMIN
  41,36,WE ‘IMMA JENZEGANNEKE MINE ESH-SHEJTANI NEZGUN FASTA’IDH BILLAHI ‘INNEHU HUWE ES-SEMI’UL-’ALIMU
  41,37,WE MIN ‘AJATIHIL-LEJLU WE EN-NEHARU WE ESH-SHEMSU WEL-KAMERU LA TESXHUDU LILSHSHEMSI WE LA LILKAMERI WE ESXHUDU LILLAHIL-LEDHI HALEKAHUNNE ‘IN KUNTUM ‘IJAHU TA’BUDUNE
  41,38,FE’INI ESTEKBERU FE-EL-LEDHINE ‘INDE RABBIKE JUSEBBIHUNE LEHU BIL-LEJLI WE EN-NEHARI WE HUM LA JES’EMUNE
  41,39,WE MIN ‘AJATIHI ‘ENNEKE TERAL-’ERDE HASHI’ATEN FE’IDHA ‘ENZELNA ‘ALEJHAL-MA’E EHTEZZET WE REBET ‘INNEL-LEDHI ‘EHJAHA LEMUHJIL-MEWTA ‘INNEHU ‘ALA KULLI SHEJ’IN KADIRUN
  41,40,‘INNEL-LEDHINE JULHIDUNE FI ‘AJATINA LA JEHFEWNE ‘ALEJNA ‘EFEMEN JULKA FI EN-NARI HAJRUN ‘EM MEN JE’TI ‘AMINÆN JEWMEL-KIJAMETI A’MELU MA SHI’TUM ‘INNEHU BIMA TA’MELUNE BESIRUN
  41,41,‘INNEL-LEDHINE KEFERU BIDH-DHIKRI LEMMA XHA’EHUM WE ‘INNEHU LEKITABUN ‘AZIZUN
  41,42,LA JE’TIHIL-BATILU MIN BEJNI JEDEJHI WE LA MIN HALFIHI TENZILUN MIN HEKIMIN HEMIDIN
  41,43,MA JUKALU LEKE ‘ILLA MA KAD KILE LILRRUSULI MIN KABLIKE ‘INNE REBBEKE LEDHU MEGFIRETIN WE DHU ‘IKABIN ‘ELIMIN
  41,44,WE LEW XHE’ALNAHU KUR’ANÆN ‘A’XHEMIJÆN LEKALU LEWLA FUSSILET ‘AJATUHU ‘E’A’XHEMIJUN WE ‘AREBIJUN KUL HUWE LILLEDHINE ‘AMENU HUDEN WE SHIFA’UN WEL-LEDHINE LA JU’UMINUNE FI ‘ADHANIHIM WEKRUN WE HUWE ‘ALEJHIM ‘AMEN ‘ULA’IKE JUNADEWNE MIN MEKANIN BA’IDIN
  41,45,WE LEKAD ‘ATEJNA MUSAL-KITABE FAHTULIFE FIHI WE LEWLA KELIMETUN SEBEKAT MIN RABBIKE LEKUDIJE BEJNEHUM WE ‘INNEHUM LEFI SHEKKIN MINHU MURIBIN
  41,46,MEN ‘AMILE SALIHÆN FELINEFSIHI WE MEN ‘ESA’E FE’ALEJHA WE MA REBBUKE BIDHELLAMIN LIL’ABIDI
  41,47,‘ILEJHI JUREDDU ‘ILMU ES-SA’ATI WE MA TEHRUXHU MIN THEMERATIN MIN ‘EKMAMIHA WE MA TEHMILU MIN ‘UNTHA WE LA TEDA’U ‘ILLA BI’ILMIHI WE JEWME JUNADIHIM ‘EJNE SHUREKA’I KALU ‘ADHENNAKE MA MINNA MIN SHEHIDIN
  41,48,WE DELLE ‘ANHUM MA KANU JED’UNE MIN KABLU WE DHENNU MA LEHUM MIN MEHISIN
  41,49,LA JES’EMUL-’INSANU MIN DU’A’IL-HAJRI WE ‘IN MESSEHU ESH-SHERRU FEJE’USUN KANUTUN
  41,50,WE LE’IN ‘EDHEKNAHU REHMETEN MINNA MIN BA’DI DERRA’E MESSET/HU LEJEKULENNE HADHA LI WE MA ‘EDHUNNU ES-SA’ATE KA’IMETEN WE LE’IN RUXHI’TU ‘ILA RABBI ‘INNE LI ‘INDEHU LELHUSNA FELENUNEBBI’ENNEL-LEDHINE KEFERU BIMA ‘AMILU WE LENUDHIKANNEHUM MIN ‘ADHABIN GALI
  41,51,WE ‘IDHA ‘EN’AMNA ‘ALEL-’INSANI ‘A’REDE WE NE’A BIXHANIBIHI WE ‘IDHA MESSEHU ESH-SHERRU FEDHU DU’A’IN ‘ARIDIN
  41,52,KUL ‘ERE’EJTUM ‘IN KANE MIN ‘INDI ELLAHI THUMME KEFERTUM BIHI MEN ‘EDELLU MIMMEN HUWE FI SHIKAKIN BA’IDIN
  41,53,SENURIHIM ‘AJATINA FIL-’AFAKI WE FI ‘ENFUSIHIM HETTA JETEBEJJENE LEHUM ‘ENNEHUL-HEKKU ‘EWELEM JEKFI BIREBBIKE ‘ENNEHU ‘ALA KULLI SHEJ’IN SHEHIDUN
  41,54,‘ELA ‘INNEHUM FI MIRJETIN MIN LIKA’I RABBIHIM ‘ELA ‘INNEHU BIKULLI SHEJ’IN MUHITUN
  42,1,HA-MIM
  42,2,‘SK
  42,3,KEDHALIKE JUHI ‘ILEJKE WE ‘ILAL-LEDHINE MIN KABLIKEL-LAHUL-’AZIZUL-HEKIMU
  42,4,LEHU MA FI ES-SEMAWATI WE MA FIL-’ERDI WE HUWEL-’ALIJUL-’ADHIMU
  42,5,TEKADU ES-SEMAWATU JETEFETTERNE MIN FEWKIHINNE WEL-MELA’IKETU JUSEBBIHUNE BIHEMDI RABBIHIM WE JESTEGFIRUNE LIMEN FIL-’ERDI ‘ELA ‘INNALL-LLAHE HUWEL-GAFURU ER-REHIMU
  42,6,WEL-LEDHINE ETTEHADHU MIN DUNIHI ‘EWLIJA’EL-LAHU HEFIDHUN ‘ALEJHIM WE MA ‘ENTE ‘ALEJHIM BIWEKILIN
  42,7,WE KEDHELIKE ‘EWHEJNA ‘ILEJKE KUR’ANÆN ‘AREBIJÆN LITUNDHIRE ‘UMMEL-KURA WE MEN HEWLEHA WE TUNDHIRE JEWMEL-XHEM’I LA REJBE FIHI FERIKUN FIL-XHENNETI WE FERIKUN FI ES-SA’IRI
  42,8,WE LEW SHA’EL-LAHU LEXHE’ALEHUM ‘UMMETEN WAHIDETEN WE LEKIN JUDHILU MEN JESHA’U FI REHMETIHI WE EDH-DHALIMUNE MA LEHUM MIN WE LIJIN WE LA NESIRIN
  42,9,‘EM ETTEHADHU MIN DUNIHI ‘EWLIJA’E FE-ELLAHU HUWEL-WELIJU WE HUWE JUHJIL-MEWTA WE HUWE ‘ALA KULLI SHEJ’IN KADIRUN
  42,10,WE MA EHTELEFTUM FIHI MIN SHEJ’IN FEHUKMUHU ‘ILA ELLAHI DHELIKUMU ELLAHU RABBI ‘ALEJHI TEWEKKELTU WE ‘ILEJHI ‘UNIBU
  42,11,FATIRU ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI XHE’ALE LEKUM MIN ‘ENFUSIKUM ‘EZWAXHÆN WE MINEL-’EN’AM ‘EZWAXHÆN JEDHRE’UUKUM FIHI LEJSE KEMITHLIHI SHEJ’UN WE HUWE ES-SEMI’UL-BESIRU
  42,12,LEHU MEKALIDU ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI JEBSUTU ER-RIZKA LIMEN JESHA’U WE JEKDIRU ‘INNEHU BIKULLI SHEJ’IN ‘ALIMUN
  42,13,SHERE’A LEKUM MINE ED-DINI MA WESSA BIHI NUHÆN WEL-LEDHI ‘EWHEJNA ‘ILEJKE WE MA WESSEJNA BIHI ‘IBRAHIME WE MUSA WE ‘ISA ‘EN ‘EKIMU ED-DINE WE LA TETEFERREKU FIHI KEBURE ‘ALEL-MUSHRIKINE MA TED’UHUM ‘ILEJHI ELLAHU JEXHTEBI ‘ILEJHI MEN JESHA’U WE JEHDI ‘ILE
  42,14,WE MA TEFERREKU ‘ILLA MIN BA’DI MA XHA’EHUMUL-’ILMU BEGJÆN BEJNEHUM WE LEWLA KELIMETUN SEBEKAT MIN RABBIKE ‘ILA ‘EXHELIN MUSEMMEN LEKUDIJE BEJNEHUM WE ‘INNEL-LEDHINE ‘URITHUL-KITABE MIN BA’DIHIM LEFI SHEKKIN MINHU MURIBIN
  42,15,FELIDHELIKE FAD’U WE ESTEKIM KEMA ‘UMIRTE WE LA TETTEBI’ ‘EHWA’EHUM WE KUL ‘AMENTU BIMA ‘ENZELEL-LAHU MIN KITABIN WE ‘UMIRTU LI’’DILE BEJNEKUMU ELLAHU REBBUNA WE REBBUKUM LENA ‘A’MALUNA WE LEKUM ‘A’MALUKUM LA HUXHXHETE BEJNENA WE BEJNEKUMU ELLAHU JEXHMA’U
  42,16,WEL-LEDHINE JUHAXHXHUNE FI ELLAHI MIN BA’DI MA ESTUXHIBE LEHU HUXHXHETUHUM DAHIDETUN ‘INDE RABBIHIM WE ‘ALEJHIM GADEBUN WE LEHUM ‘ADHABUN SHEDIDUN
  42,17,ELLAHUL-LEDHI ‘ENZELEL-KITABE BIL-HEKKI WEL-MIZANE WE MA JUDRIKE LE’ALLE ES-SA’ATE KARIBUN
  42,18,JESTA’XHILU BIHAL-LEDHINE LA JU’UMINUNE BIHA WEL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU MUSHFIKUNE MINHA WE JA’LEMUNE ‘ENNEHAL-HEKKU ‘ELA ‘INNEL-LEDHINE JUMARUNE FI ES-SA’ATI LEFI DELALIN BA’IDIN
  42,19,ELLAHU LETIFUN BI’IBADIHI JERZUKU MEN JESHA’U WE HUWEL-KAWIJUL-’AZIZU
  42,20,MEN KANE JURIDU HERTHEL-’AHIRETI NEZID LEHU FI HERTHIHI WE MEN KANE JURIDU HERTHE ED-DUNJA NU’UTIHI MINHA WE MA LEHU FIL-’AHIRETI MIN NESIBIN
  42,21,‘EM LEHUM SHUREKA’U SHERA’U LEHUM MINE ED-DINI MA LEM JE’DHEN BIHI ELLAHU WE LEWLA KELIMETUL-FESLI LEKUDIJE BEJNEHUM WE ‘INNE EDH-DHALIMINE LEHUM ‘ADHABUN ‘ELIMUN
  42,22,TERA EDH-DHALIMINE MUSHFIKINE MIMMA KESEBU WE HUWE WAKI’UN BIHIM WEL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU WE ‘AMILU ES-SALIHATI FI REWDATIL-XHENNATI LEHUM MA JESHA’UNE ‘INDE RABBIHIM DHALIKE HUWEL-FEDLUL-KEBIRU
  42,23,DHALIKEL-LEDHI JUBESHSHIRU ELLAHU ‘IBADEHUL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU WE ‘AMILU ES-SALIHATI KUL LA ‘ES’ELUKUM ‘ALEJHI ‘EXHRÆN ‘ILLAL-MEWEDDETE FIL-KURBA WE MEN JEKTERIF HESENETEN NEZID LEHU FIHA HUSNÆN ‘INNALL-LLAHE GAFURUN SHEKURUN
  42,24,‘EM JEKULUNE EFTERA ‘ALA ELLAHI KEDHIBÆN FE’IN JESHE’I ELLAHU JEHTIM ‘ALA KALBIKE WE JEMHU ELLAHUL-BATILE WE JUHIKKUL-HEKKA BIKELIMATIHI ‘INNEHU ‘ALIMUN BIDHATI ES-SUDURI
  42,25,WE HUWEL-LEDHI JEKBELUT-TEWBET ‘AN ‘IBADIHI WE JA’FU ‘ANI ES-SEJJI’ATI WE JA’LEMU MA TEF’ALUNE
  42,26,WE JESTEXHIBUL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU WE ‘AMILU ES-SALIHATI WE JEZIDUHUM MIN FEDLIHI WEL-KAFIRUNE LEHUM ‘ADHABUN SHEDIDUN
  42,27,WE LEW BESETEL-LAHU ER-RIZKA LI’IBADIHI LEBEGAW FIL-’ERDI WE LEKIN JUNEZZILU BIKADERIN MA JESHA’U ‘INNEHU BI’IBADIHI HABIRUN BESIRUN
  42,28,WE HUWEL-LEDHI JUNEZZILUL-GAJTHE MIN BA’DI MA KANETU WE JENSHURU REHMETEHU WE HUWEL-WELIJUL-HEMIDU
  42,29,WE MIN ‘AJATIHI HALKU ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI WE MA BETHTHE FIHIMA MIN DABBETIN WE HUWE ‘ALA XHEM’IHIM ‘IDHA JESHA’U KADIRUN
  42,30,WE MA ‘ESABEKUM MIN MUSIBETIN FEBIMA KESEBET ‘EJDIKUM WE JA’FU ‘AN KETHIRIN
  42,31,WE MA ‘ENTUM BIMU’XHIZINE FIL-’ERDI WE MA LEKUM MIN DUNI ELLAHI MIN WE LIJIN WE LA NESIRIN
  42,32,WE MIN ‘AJATIHIL-XHEWARI FIL-BEHRI KAL’A’LAMI
  42,33,‘IN JESHE’ JUSKINI ER-RIHE FEJEDHLELNE REWAKIDE ‘ALA DHEHRIHI ‘INNE FI DHALIKE LE’AJATIN LIKULLI SEBBARIN SHEKURIN
  42,34,‘EW JUBIKHUNNE BIMA KESEBU WE JA’FU ‘AN KETHIRIN
  42,35,WE JA’LEMEL-LEDHINE JUXHADILUNE FI ‘AJATINA MA LEHUM MIN MEHISIN
  42,36,FEMA ‘UTITUM MIN SHEJ’IN FEMETA’UL-HEJÆTI ED-DUNJA WE MA ‘INDEL-LAHI HAJRUN WE ‘EBKA LILLEDHINE ‘AMENU WE ‘ALA RABBIHIM JETEWEKKELUNE
  42,37,WEL-LEDHINE JEXHTENIBUNE KEBA’IREL-’ITHMI WEL-FEWAHISHE WE ‘IDHA MA GADIBU HUM JEGFIRUNE
  42,38,WEL-LEDHINE ESTEXHABU LIREBBIHIM WE ‘EKAMU ES-SELÆTE WE ‘EMRUHUM SHURA BEJNEHUM WE MIMMA REZEKNAHUM JUNFIKUNE
  42,39,WEL-LEDHINE ‘IDHA ‘ESABEHUMUL-BEGJU HUM JENTESIRUNE
  42,40,WE XHEZA’U SEJJI’ETIN SEJJI’ETUN MITHLUHA FEMEN ‘AFA WE ‘ESLEHE FE’EXHRUHU ‘ALA ELLAHI ‘INNEHU LA JUHIBBU EDH-DHALIMINE
  42,41,WE LEMENI ENTESERE BA’DE DHULMIHI FE’ULA’IKE MA ‘ALEJHIM MIN SEBILIN
  42,42,‘INNEMA ES-SEBILU ‘ALEL-LEDHINE JEDHLIMUNE EN-NASE WE JEBGUNE FIL-’ERDI BIGAJRIL-HEKKI ‘ULA’IKE LEHUM ‘ADHABUN ‘ELIMUN
  42,43,WE LEMEN SEBERE WE GAFERE ‘INNE DHALIKE LEMIN ‘AZMIL-’UMURI
  42,44,WE MEN JUDLILI ELLAHU FEMA LEHU MIN WE LIJIN MIN BA’DIHI WE TERA EDH-DHALIMINE LEMMA RE’EWL-’ADHABE JEKULUNE HEL ‘ILA MEREDDIN MIN SEBILIN
  42,45,WE TERAHUM JU’REDUNE ‘ALEJHA HASHI’INE MINE EDH-DHULLI JENDHURUNE MIN TERFIN HAFIJIN WE KALEL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU ‘INNEL-HASIRINEL-LEDHINE HASIRU ‘ENFUSEHUM WE ‘EHLIHIM JEWMEL-KIJAMETI ‘ELA ‘INNE EDH-DHALIMINE FI ‘ADHABIN MUKIMIN
  42,46,WE MA KANE LEHUM MIN ‘EWLIJA’E JENSURUNEHUM MIN DUNI ELLAHI WE MEN JUDLILI ELLAHU FEMA LEHU MIN SEBILIN
  42,47,ESTEXHIBU LIREBBIKUM MIN KABLI ‘EN JE’TIJE JEWMUN LA MEREDDE LEHU MINEL-LAHI MA LEKUM MIN MELXHE’IIN JEWME’IDHIN WE MA LEKUM MIN NEKIRIN
  42,48,FE’IN ‘A’REDU FEMA ‘ERSELNAKE ‘ALEJHIM HEFIDHÆN ‘IN ‘ALEJKE ‘ILLAL-BELAGU WE ‘INNA ‘IDHA ‘EDHEKNAL-’INSANE MINNA REHMETEN FERIHE BIHA WE ‘IN TUSIBHUM SEJJI’ETUN BIMA KADDEMET ‘EJDIHIM FE’INNEL-’INSANE KEFURUN
  42,49,LILLAHI MULKU ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI JEHLUKU MA JESHA’U JEHEBU LIMEN JESHA’U ‘INATHÆN WE JEHEBU LIMEN JESHA’U EDH-DHUKURE
  42,50,‘EW JUZEWWIXHUHUM DHUKRANÆN WE ‘INATHÆN WE JEXH’ALU MEN JESHA’U ‘AKIMÆN ‘INNEHU ‘ALIMUN KADIRUN
  42,51,WE MA KANE LIBESHERIN ‘EN JUKELLIMEHU ELLAHU ‘ILLA WEHJÆN ‘EW MIN WERA’I HIXHABIN ‘EW JURSILE RESULÆN FEJUHIJE BI’IDHNIHI MA JESHA’U ‘INNEHU ‘ALIJUN HEKIMUN
  42,52,WE KEDHELIKE ‘EWHEJNA ‘ILEJKE RUHÆN MIN ‘EMRINA MA KUNTE TEDRI MAL-KITABU WE LAL-’IMANU WE LEKIN XHE’ALNAHU NURÆN NEHDI BIHI MEN NESHA’U MIN ‘IBADINA WE ‘INNEKE LETEHDI ‘ILA SIRATIN MUSTEKIMIN
  42,53,SIRATI ELLAHIL-LEDHI LEHU MA FI ES-SEMAWATI WE MA FIL-’ERDI ‘ELA ‘ILA ELLAHI TESIRUL-’UMURU
  43,1,HA-MIM
  43,2,WEL-KITABIL-MUBINI
  43,3,‘INNA XHE’ALNAHU KUR’ANÆN ‘AREBIJÆN LE’ALLEKUM TA’KILUNE
  43,4,WE ‘INNEHU FI ‘UMMIL-KITABI LEDEJNA LE’ALIJUN HEKIMUN
  43,5,‘EFENEDRIBU ‘ANKUMU EDH-DHIKRE SEFHÆN ‘EN KUNTUM KAWMÆN MUSRIFINE
  43,6,WE KEM ‘ERSELNA MIN NEBIJIN FIL-’EWWELINE
  43,7,WE MA JE’TIHIM MIN NEBIJIN ‘ILLA KANU BIHI JESTEHZI’UN
  43,8,FE’EHLEKNA ‘ESHEDDE MINHUM BETSHÆN WE MEDA METHELUL-’EWWELINE
  43,9,WE LE’IN SE’ELTEHUM MEN HALEKA ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDE LEJEKULUNNE HALEKAHUNNEL-’AZIZUL-’ALIMU
  43,10,EL-LEDHI XHE’ALE LEKUMUL-’ERDE MEHDÆN WE XHE’ALE LEKUM FIHA SUBULÆN LE’ALLEKUM TEHTEDUNE
  43,11,WEL-LEDHI NEZZELE MINE ES-SEMA’I MA’EN BIKADERIN FE’ENSHERNA BIHI BELDETEN MEJTÆN KEDHALIKE TUHREXHUNE
  43,12,WEL-LEDHI HALEKAL-’EZWAXHE KULLEHA WE XHE’ALE LEKUM MINEL-FULKI WEL-’EN’AM MA TERKEBUNE
  43,13,LITESTEWU ‘ALA DHUHURIHI THUMME TEDHKURU NI’METE RABBIKUM ‘IDHA ESTEWEJTUM ‘ALEJHI WE TEKULU SUBHANEL-LEDHI SEHHARE LENA HADHA WE MA KUNNA LEHU MUKRININE
  43,14,WE ‘INNA ‘ILA RABBINA LEMUNKALIBUNE
  43,15,WE XHE’ALU LEHU MIN ‘IBADIHI XHUZ’ÆN ‘INNEL-’INSANE LEKEFURUN MUBINUN
  43,16,‘EM ETTEHADHE MIMMA JEHLUKU BENATIN WE ‘ESFAKUM BIL-BENINE
  43,17,WE ‘IDHA BUSHSHIRE ‘EHEDUHUM BIMA DEREBE LILRREHMENI METHELÆN DHELLE WEXHHUHU MUSWEDDÆN WE HUWE KEDHIMUN
  43,18,‘EWEMEN JUNESHSHE’U FIL-HILJETI WE HUWE FIL-HISAMI GAJRU MUBININ
  43,19,WE XHE’ALUL-MELA’IKETEL-LEDHINE HUM ‘IBADU ER-REHMANI ‘INATHÆN ‘ESHEHIDU HALKAHUM SETUKTEBU SHEHADETUHUM WE JUS’ELUNE
  43,20,WE KALU LEW SHA’E ER-REHMANU MA ‘ABEDNAHUM MA LEHUM BIDHALIKE MIN ‘ILMIN ‘IN HUM ‘ILLA JEHRUSUNE
  43,21,‘EM ‘ATEJNAHUM KITABÆN MIN KABLIHI FEHUM BIHI MUSTEMSIKUNE
  43,22,BEL KALU ‘INNA WEXHEDNA ‘ABA’ENA ‘ALA ‘UMMETIN WE ‘INNA ‘ALA ‘ATHARIHIM MUHTEDUNE
  43,23,WE KEDHELIKE MA ‘ERSELNA MIN KABLIKE FI KARJETIN MIN NEDHIRIN ‘ILLA KALE MUTREFUHA ‘INNA WEXHEDNA ‘ABA’ENA ‘ALA ‘UMMETIN WE ‘INNA ‘ALA ‘ATHARIHIM MUKTEDUNE
  43,24,KALE ‘EWELEW XHI’TUKUM BI’EHDA MIMMA WEXHEDTUM ‘ALEJHI ‘ABA’EKUM KALU ‘INNA BIMA ‘URSILTUM BIHI KAFIRUNE
  43,25,FANTEKAMNA MINHUM FANDHUR KEJFE KANE ‘AKIBETUL-MUKEDHDHIBINE
  43,26,WE ‘IDH KALE ‘IBRAHIMU LI’EBIHI WE KAWMIHI ‘INNENI BERA’UN MIMMA TA’BUDUNE
  43,27,‘ILLAL-LEDHI FETERENI FE’INNEHU SEJEHDINI
  43,28,WE XHE’ALEHA KELIMETEN BAKIJETEN FI ‘AKIBIHI LE’ALLEHUM JERXHI’UNE
  43,29,BEL METTA’TU HA’UULA’ WE ‘ABA’EHUM HETTA XHA’EHUMUL-HEKKU WE RESULUN MUBINUN
  43,30,WE LEMMA XHA’EHUMUL-HEKKU KALU HADHA SIHRUN WE ‘INNA BIHI KAFIRUNE
  43,31,WE KALU LEWLA NUZZILE HADHAL-KUR’ANU ‘ALA REXHULIN MINEL-KARJETEJNI ‘ADHIMIN
  43,32,‘EHUM JEKSIMUNE REHMETE RABBIKE NEHNU KASEMNA BEJNEHUM MA’ISHETEHUM FIL-HEJÆTI ED-DUNJA WE REFA’NA BA’DEHUM FEWKA BA’DIN DEREXHATIN LIJETTEHIDHE BA’DUHUM BA’DÆN SUHRIJÆN WE REHMETU RABBIKE HAJRUN MIMMA JEXHMA’UNE
  43,33,WE LEWLA ‘EN JEKUNE EN-NASU ‘UMMETEN WAHIDETEN LEXHE’ALNA LIMEN JEKFURU BIR-REHMENI LIBUJUTIHIM SUKUFÆN MIN FEDDETIN WE MA’ARIXHE ‘ALEJHA JEDHHERUNE
  43,34,WE LIBUJUTIHIM ‘EBWABÆN WE SURURÆN ‘ALEJHA JETTEKI’UNE
  43,35,WE ZUHRUFÆN WE ‘IN KULLU DHALIKE LEMMA META’UL-HEJÆTI ED-DUNJA WEL-’AHIRETU ‘INDE RABBIKE LILMUTTEKINE
  43,36,WE MEN JA’SHU ‘AN DHIKRI ER-REHMANI NUKAJJID LEHU SHEJTANÆN FEHUWE LEHU KARINUN
  43,37,WE ‘INNEHUM LEJESUDDUNEHUM ‘ANI ES-SEBILI WE JEHSEBUNE ‘ENNEHUM MUHTEDUNE
  43,38,HETTA ‘IDHA XHA’ENA KALE JA LEJTE BEJNI WE BEJNEKE BU’DEL-MESHRIKAJNI FEBI’SEL-KARINU
  43,39,WE LEN JENFE’AKUMUL-JEWME ‘IDH DHELEMTUM ‘ENNEKUM FIL-’ADHABI MUSHTERIKUNE
  43,40,‘EFE’ENTE TUSMI’U ES-SUMME ‘EW TEHDIL-’UMJE WE MEN KANE FI DELALIN MUBININ
  43,41,FE’IMMA NEDH/HEBENNE BIKE FE’INNA MINHUM MUNTEKIMUNE
  43,42,‘EW NURIJENNEKEL-LEDHI WE’ADNAHUM FE’INNA ‘ALEJHIM MUKTEDIRUNE
  43,43,FASTEMSIK BIEL-LEDHI ‘UHIJE ‘ILEJKE ‘INNEKE ‘ALA SIRATIN MUSTEKIMIN
  43,44,WE ‘INNEHU LEDHIKRUN LEKE WE LIKAWMIKE WE SEWFE TUS’ELUNE
  43,45,WE ES’EL MEN ‘ERSELNA MIN KABLIKE MIN RUSULINA ‘EXHE’ALNA MIN DUNI ER-REHMANI ‘ALIHETEN JU’BEDUNE
  43,46,WE LEKAD ‘ERSELNA MUSA BI’AJATINA ‘ILA FIR’AWNE WE MELE’IHI FEKALE ‘INNI RESULU RABBIL-’ALEMINE
  43,47,FELEMMA XHA’EHUM BI’AJATINA ‘IDHA HUM MINHA JEDHEKUNE
  43,48,WE MA NURIHIM MIN ‘AJETIN ‘ILLA HIJE ‘EKBERU MIN ‘UHTIHA WE ‘EHADHNAHUM BIL-’ADHABI LE’ALLEHUM JERXHI’UNE
  43,49,WE KALU JA ‘EJJUHA ES-SAHIRU ED’U LENA REBBEKE BIMA ‘AHIDE ‘INDEKE ‘INNENA LEMUHTEDUN
  43,50,FELEMMA KESHEFNA ‘ANHUMUL-’ADHABE ‘IDHA HUM JENKUTHUNE
  43,51,WE NADA FIR’AWNU FI KAWMIHI KALE JA KAWMI ‘ELEJSE LI MULKU MISRE WE HEDHIHIL-’ENHARU TEXHRI MIN TEHTI ‘EFELA TUBSIRUNE
  43,52,‘EM ‘ENA HAJRUN MIN HADHAL-LEDHI HUWE MEHINUN WE LA JEKADU JUBINU
  43,53,FELEWLA ‘ULKIJE ‘ALEJHI ‘ESWIRETUN MIN DHEHEBIN ‘EW XHA’E ME’AHUL-MELA’IKETU MUKTERININE
  43,54,FASTEHAFFE KAWMEHU FE’ETA’UHU ‘INNEHUM KANU KAWMÆN FASIKINE
  43,55,FELEMMA ‘ASEFUNA ENTEKAMNA MINHUM FE’EGREKNAHUM ‘EXHMA’INE
  43,56,FEXHE’ALNAHUM SELEFÆN WE METHELÆN LIL’AHIRINE
  43,57,WE LEMMA DURIBE EBNU MERJEME METHELÆN ‘IDHA KAWMUKE MINHU JESIDDUNE
  43,58,WE KALU ‘E’ALIHETUNA HAJRUN ‘EM HUWE MA DEREBUHU LEKE ‘ILLA XHEDELÆN BEL HUM KAWMUN HASIMUNE
  43,59,‘IN HUWE ‘ILLA ‘ABDUN ‘EN’AMNA ‘ALEJHI WE XHE’ALNAHU METHELÆN LIBENI ‘ISRA’ILE
  43,60,WE LEW NESHA’U LEXHE’ALNA MINKUM MELA’IKETEN FIL-’ERDI JEHLUFUNE
  43,61,WE ‘INNEHU LA’ILMUN LILSSA’ATI FELA TEMTERUNNE BIHA WE ETTEBI’UNI HADHA SIRATUN MUSTEKIMUN
  43,62,WE LA JESUDDENNEKUMU ESH-SHEJTANU ‘INNEHU LEKUM ‘ADUWUN MUBINUN
  43,63,WE LEMMA XHA’E ‘ISA BIL-BEJJINATI KALE KAD XHI’TUKUM BIL-HIKMETI WE LI’EBEJJINE LEKUM BA’DEL-LEDHI TEHTELIFUNE FIHI FE ETTEKU ELLAHE WE ‘ETI’UNI
  43,64,‘INNALL-LLAHE HUWE RABBI WE REBBUKUM FA’BUDUHU HADHA SIRATUN MUSTEKIMUN
  43,65,FAHTELEFEL-’EHZABU MIN BEJNIHIM FEWEJLUN LILLEDHINE DHELEMU MIN ‘ADHABI JEWMIN ‘ELIMIN
  43,66,HEL JENDHURUNE ‘ILLA ES-SA’ATE ‘EN TE’TIJEHUM BEGTETEN WE HUM LA JESH’URUNE
  43,67,EL-’EHILLA’U JEWME’IDHIN BA’DUHUM LIBA’DIN ‘ADUWUN ‘ILLAL-MUTTEKINE
  43,68,JA ‘IBADI LA HAWFUN ‘ALEJKUMUL-JEWME WE LA ‘ENTUM TEHZENUNE
  43,69,EL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU BI’AJATINA WE KANU MUSLIMINE
  43,70,EDHULUL-XHENNETE ‘ENTUM WE ‘EZWAXHUKUM TUHBERUNE
  43,71,JUTAFU ‘ALEJHIM BISIHAFIN MIN DHEHEBIN WE ‘EKWABIN WE FIHA MA TESHTEHIHIL-’ENFUSU WE TELEDHDHUL-’A’JUNU WE ‘ENTUM FIHA HALIDUNE
  43,72,WE TILKEL-XHENNETU ELLETI ‘URITHTUMUHA BIMA KUNTUM TA’MELUNE
  43,73,LEKUM FIHA FAKIHETUN KETHIRETUN MINHA TE’KULUNE
  43,74,‘INNEL-MUXHRIMINE FI ‘ADHABI XHEHENNEME HALIDUN
  43,75,LA JUFETTERU ‘ANHUM WE HUM FIHI MUBLISUNE
  43,76,WE MA DHELEMNAHUM WE LEKIN KANU HUMU EDH-DHALIMINE
  43,77,WE NADEW JA MALIKU LIJEKDI ‘ALEJNA REBBUKE KALE ‘INNEKUM MAKITHUNE
  43,78,LEKAD XHI’NAKUM BIL-HEKKI WE LEKINNE ‘EKTHEREKUM LILHEKKI KARIHUNE
  43,79,‘EM ‘EBREMU ‘EMRÆN FE’INNA MUBRIMUNE
  43,80,‘EM JEHSEBUNE ‘ENNA LA NESMA’U SIRREHUM WE NEXHWAHUM BELA WE RUSULUNA LEDEJHIM JEKTUBUNE
  43,81,KUL ‘IN KANE LILRREHMENI WELEDUN FE’ENA ‘EWWELUL-’ABIDINE
  43,82,SUBHANE RABBI ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI RABBIL-’ARSHI ‘AMMA JESIFUNE
  43,83,FEDHERHUM JEHUDU WE JEL’ABU HETTA JULAKU JEWMEHUMUL-LEDHI JU’ADUNE
  43,84,WE HUWEL-LEDHI FI ES-SEMA’I ‘ILEHUN WE FIL-’ERDI ‘ILEHUN WE HUWEL-HEKIMUL-’ALIMU
  43,85,WE TEBAREKEL-LEDHI LEHU MULKU ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI WE MA BEJNEHUMA WE ‘INDEHU ‘ILMU ES-SA’ATI WE ‘ILEJHI TURXHA’UNE
  43,86,WE LA JEMLIKUL-LEDHINE JED’UNE MIN DUNIHI ESH-SHEFA’ATE ‘ILLA MEN SHEHIDE BIL-HEKKI WE HUM JA’LEMUNE
  43,87,WE LE’IN SE’ELTEHUM MEN HALEKAHUM LEJEKULUNNEL-LAHU FE’ENNA JU’UFEKUNE
  43,88,WE KILIHI JA RABBI ‘INNE HA’UULA’ KAWMUN LA JU’UMINUNE
  43,89,FASFEH ‘ANHUM WE KUL SELAMUN FESEWFE JA’LEMUNE
  44,1,HA-MIM
  44,2,WEL-KITABIL-MUBINI
  44,3,‘INNA ‘ENZELNAHU FI LEJLETIN MUBAREKETIN ‘INNA KUNNA MUNDHIRINE
  44,4,FIHA JUFREKU KULLU ‘EMRIN HEKIMIN
  44,5,‘EMRÆN MIN ‘INDINA ‘INNA KUNNA MURSILINE
  44,6,REHMETEN MIN RABBIKE ‘INNEHU HUWE ES-SEMI’UL-’ALIMU
  44,7,REBBI ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI WE MA BEJNEHUMA ‘IN KUNTUM MUKININE
  44,8,LA ‘ILAHE ‘ILLA HUWE JUHJI WE JUMITU REBBUKUM WE REBBU ‘ABA’IKUMUL-’EWWELINE
  44,9,BEL HUM FI SHEKKIN JEL’ABUNE
  44,10,FARTEKIB JEWME TE’TI ES-SEMA’U BIDUHANIN MUBININ
  44,11,JEGSHA EN-NASE HADHA ‘ADHABUN ‘ELIMUN
  44,12,REBBENA EKSHIF ‘ANNAL-’ADHABE ‘INNA MU’UMINUNE
  44,13,‘ENNA LEHUMU EDH-DHIKRA WE KAD XHA’EHUM RESULUN MUBINUN
  44,14,THUMME TEWELLEW ‘ANHU WE KALU MU’ALLEMUN MEXHNUNUN
  44,15,‘INNA KASHIFUL-’ADHABI KALILÆN ‘INNEKUM ‘A’IDUNE
  44,16,JEWME NEBTISHUL-BETSHETEL-KUBRA ‘INNA MUNTEKIMUNE
  44,17,WE LEKAD FETENNA KABLEHUM KAWME FIR’AWNE WE XHA’EHUM RESULUN KERIMUN
  44,18,‘EN ‘EDDU ‘ILEJJE ‘IBADEL-LAHI ‘INNI LEKUM RESULUN ‘EMINUN
  44,19,WE ‘EN LA TA’LU ‘ALA ELLAHI ‘INNI ‘ATIKUM BISULTANIN MUBININ
  44,20,WE ‘INNI ‘UDHTU BIREBBI WE RABBIKUM ‘EN TERXHUMUNI
  44,21,WE ‘IN LEM TU’UMINU LI FA’TEZILUNI
  44,22,FEDA’A REBBEHU ‘ENNE HA’UULA’ KAWMUN MUXHRIMUNE
  44,23,FE’ESRI BI’IBADI LEJLÆN ‘INNEKUM MUTTEBA’UNE
  44,24,WE ETRUKIL-BEHRE REHWEN ‘INNEHUM XHUNDUN MUGREKUNE
  44,25,KEM TEREKU MIN XHENNATIN WE ‘UJUNIN
  44,26,WE ZURU’IN WE MEKAMIN KERIMIN
  44,27,WE NA’METIN KANU FIHA FAKIHINE
  44,28,KEDHALIKE WE ‘EWRETHNAHA KAWMÆN ‘AHARINE
  44,29,FEMA BEKET ‘ALEJHIMU ES-SEMA’U WEL-’ERDU WE MA KANU MUNDHERINE
  44,30,WE LEKAD NEXHXHEJNA BENI ‘ISRA’ILE MINEL-’ADHABIL-MUHINI
  44,31,MIN FIR’AWNE ‘INNEHU KANE ‘ALIÆN MINEL-MUSRIFINE
  44,32,WE LEKADI EHTERNAHUM ‘ALA ‘ILMIN ‘ALEL-’ALEMINE
  44,33,WE ‘ATEJNAHUM MINEL-’AJATI MA FIHI BELA’UN MUBINUN
  44,34,‘INNE HA’UULA’ LEJEKULUNE
  44,35,‘IN HIJE ‘ILLA MEWTETUNAL-’ULA WE MA NEHNU BIMUNSHERINE
  44,36,FE’TU BI’ABA’INA ‘IN KUNTUM SADIKINE
  44,37,‘EHUM HAJRUN ‘EM KAWMU TUBBA’IN WEL-LEDHINE MIN KABLIHIM ‘EHLEKNAHUM ‘INNEHUM KANU MUXHRIMINE
  44,38,WE MA HALEKNA ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDE WE MA BEJNEHUMA LA’IBINE
  44,39,MA HALEKNAHUMA ‘ILLA BIL-HEKKI WE LEKINNE ‘EKTHEREHUM LA JA’LEMUNE
  44,40,‘INNE JEWMEL-FESLI MIKATUHUM ‘EXHMA’INE
  44,41,JEWME LA JUGNI MEWLEN ‘AN MEWLEN SHEJ’ÆN WE LA HUM JUNSERUNE
  44,42,‘ILLA MEN REHIMEL-LAHU ‘INNEHU HUWEL-’AZIZU ER-REHIMU
  44,43,‘INNE SHEXHERETE EZ-ZEKKUMI
  44,44,TA’AMUL-’ETHIMI
  44,45,KALMUHLI JEGLI FIL-BUTUNI
  44,46,KEGALJIL-HEMIMI
  44,47,HUDHUHU FA’TILUHU ‘ILA SEWA’IL-XHEHIMI
  44,48,THUMME SUBBU FEWKA RE’SIHI MIN ‘ADHABIL-HEMIMI
  44,49,DHUK ‘INNEKE ‘ENTEL-’AZIZUL-KERIMU
  44,50,‘INNE HADHA MA KUNTUM BIHI TEMTERUNE
  44,51,‘INNEL-MUTTEKINE FI MEKAMIN ‘EMININ
  44,52,FI XHENNATIN WE ‘UJUNIN
  44,53,JELBESUNE MIN SUNDUSIN WE ‘ISTEBREKIN MUTEKABILINE
  44,54,KEDHALIKE WE ZEWWEXHNAHUM BIHURIN ‘ININ
  44,55,JED’UNE FIHA BIKULLI FAKIHETIN ‘AMININE
  44,56,LA JEDHUKUNE FIHAL-MEWTE ‘ILLAL-MEWTETEL-’ULA WE WEKAHUM ‘ADHABEL-XHEHIMI
  44,57,FEDLÆN MIN RABBIKE DHALIKE HUWEL-FEWZUL-’ADHIMU
  44,58,FE’INNEMA JESSERNAHU BILISANIKE LE’ALLEHUM JETEDHEKKERUNE
  44,59,FARTEKIB ‘INNEHUM MURTEKIBUNE
  45,1,HA-MIM
  45,2,TENZILUL-KITABI MINEL-LAHIL-’AZIZIL-HEKIMI
  45,3,‘INNE FI ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI LE’AJATIN LILMU’UMININE
  45,4,WE FI HALKIKUM WE MA JEBUTHTHU MIN DABBETIN ‘AJATUN LIKAWMIN JUKINUNE
  45,5,WE EHTILAFIL-LEJLI WE EN-NEHARI WE MA ‘ENZELEL-LAHU MINE ES-SEMA’I MIN RIZKIN FE’EHJA BIHIL-’ERDE BA’DE MEWTIHA WE TESRIFI ER-RIJAHI ‘AJATUN LIKAWMIN JA’KILUNE
  45,6,TILKE ‘AJATU ELLAHI NETLUHA ‘ALEJKE BIL-HEKKI FEBI’EJJI HEDITHIN BA’DEL-LAHI WE ‘AJATIHI JU’UMINUNE
  45,7,WEJLUN LIKULLI ‘EFFAKIN ‘ETHIMIN
  45,8,JESMA’U ‘AJATI ELLAHI TUTLA ‘ALEJHI THUMME JUSIRRU MUSTEKBIRÆN KE’EN LEM JESMA’HA FEBESHSHIRHU BI’ADHABIN ‘ELIMIN
  45,9,WE ‘IDHA ‘ALIME MIN ‘AJATINA SHEJ’ÆN ETTEHADHEHA HUZUEN ‘ULA’IKE LEHUM ‘ADHABUN MUHINUN
  45,10,MIN WERA’IHIM XHEHENNEMU WE LA JUGNI ‘ANHUM MA KESEBU SHEJ’ÆN WE LA MA ETTEHADHU MIN DUNI ELLAHI ‘EWLIJA’E WE LEHUM ‘ADHABUN ‘ADHIMUN
  45,11,HADHA HUDEN WEL-LEDHINE KEFERU BI’AJATI RABBIHIM LEHUM ‘ADHABUN MIN RIXHZIN ‘ELIMUN
  45,12,ELLAHUL-LEDHI SEHHARE LEKUMUL-BEHRE LITEXHRIJEL-FULKU FIHI BI’EMRIHI WE LITEBTEGU MIN FEDLIHI WE LE’ALLEKUM TESHKURUNE
  45,13,WE SEHHARE LEKUM MA FI ES-SEMAWATI WE MA FIL-’ERDI XHEMI’ÆN MINHU ‘INNE FI DHALIKE LE’AJATIN LIKAWMIN JETEFEKKERUNE
  45,14,KUL LILLEDHINE ‘AMENU JEGFIRU LILLEDHINE LA JERXHUNE ‘EJJAMEL-LAHI LIJEXHZIJE KAWMÆN BIMA KANU JEKSIBUNE
  45,15,MEN ‘AMILE SALIHÆN FELINEFSIHI WE MEN ‘ESA’E FE’ALEJHA THUMME ‘ILA RABBIKUM TURXHA’UNE
  45,16,WE LEKAD ‘ATEJNA BENI ‘ISRA’ILEL-KITABE WEL-HUKME WE EN-NUBUWETE WE REZEKNAHUM MINET-TEJJIBATI WE FEDDELNAHUM ‘ALEL-’ALEMINE
  45,17,WE ‘ATEJNAHUM BEJJINATIN MINEL-’EMRI FEMA EHTELEFU ‘ILLA MIN BA’DI MA XHA’EHUMUL-’ILMU BEGJÆN BEJNEHUM ‘INNE REBBEKE JEKDI BEJNEHUM JEWMEL-KIJAMETI FIMA KANU FIHI JEHTELIFUNE
  45,18,THUMME XHE’ALNAKE ‘ALA SHERI’ATIN MINEL-’EMRI FE ETTEBI’HA WE LA TETTEBI’ ‘EHWA’EL-LEDHINE LA JA’LEMUNE
  45,19,‘INNEHUM LEN JUGNU ‘ANKE MINEL-LAHI SHEJ’ÆN WE ‘INNE EDH-DHALIMINE BA’DUHUM ‘EWLIJA’U BA’DIN WEL-LAHU WE LIJUL-MUTTEKINE
  45,20,HADHA BESA’IRU LILNNASI WE HUDEN WE REHMETUN LIKAWMIN JUKINUNE
  45,21,‘EM HESIBEL-LEDHINE EXHTEREHU ES-SEJJI’ATI ‘EN NEXH’ALEHUM KALLEDHINE ‘AMENU WE ‘AMILU ES-SALIHATI SEWA’EN MEHJAHUM WE MEMATUHUM SA’E MA JEHKUMUNE
  45,22,WE HALEKAL-LAHU ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDE BIL-HEKKI WE LITUXHZA KULLU NEFSIN BIMA KESEBET WE HUM LA JUDHLEMUNE
  45,23,‘EFERE’EJTE MENI ETTEHADHE ‘ILEHEHU HEWAHU WE ‘EDELLEHU ELLAHU ‘ALA ‘ILMIN WE HATEME ‘ALA SEM’IHI WE KALBIHI WE XHE’ALE ‘ALA BESERIHI GISHAWETEN FEMEN JEHDIHI MIN BA’DI ELLAHI ‘EFELA TEDHEKKERUNE
  45,24,WE KALU MA HIJE ‘ILLA HEJATUNA ED-DUNJA NEMUTU WE NEHJA WE MA JUHLIKUNA ‘ILLA ED-DEHRU WE MA LEHUM BIDHALIKE MIN ‘ILMIN ‘IN HUM ‘ILLA JEDHUNNUNE
  45,25,WE ‘IDHA TUTLA ‘ALEJHIM ‘AJATUNA BEJJINATIN MA KANE HUXHXHETEHUM ‘ILLA ‘EN KALU E’TU BI’ABA’INA ‘IN KUNTUM SADIKINE
  45,26,KULI ELLAHU JUHJIKUM THUMME JUMITUKUM THUMME JEXHMA’UKUM ‘ILA JEWMIL-KIJAMETI LA REJBE FIHI WE LEKINNE ‘EKTHERE EN-NASI LA JA’LEMUNE
  45,27,WE LILLEHI MULKU ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI WE JEWME TEKUMU ES-SA’ATU JEWME’IDHIN JEHSERUL-MUBTILUNE
  45,28,WE TERA KULLE ‘UMMETIN XHATHIJETEN KULLU ‘UMMETIN TUD’A ‘ILA KITABIHAL-JEWME TUXHZEWNE MA KUNTUM TA’MELUNE
  45,29,HADHA KITABUNA JENTIKU ‘ALEJKUM BIL-HEKKI ‘INNA KUNNA NESTENSIHU MA KUNTUM TA’MELUNE
  45,30,FE’EMMAL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU WE ‘AMILU ES-SALIHATI FEJUDHILUHUM REBBUHUM FI REHMETIHI DHALIKE HUWEL-FEWZUL-MUBINU
  45,31,WE ‘EMMAL-LEDHINE KEFERU ‘EFELEM TEKUN ‘AJATI TUTLA ‘ALEJKUM FASTEKBERTUM WE KUNTUM KAWMÆN MUXHRIMINE
  45,32,WE ‘IDHA KILE ‘INNE WA’DEL-LAHI HEKKUN WE ES-SA’ATU LA REJBE FIHA KULTUM MA NEDRI MA ES-SA’ATU ‘IN NEDHUNNU ‘ILLA DHENNÆN WE MA NEHNU BIMUSTEJKININE
  45,33,WE BEDA LEHUM SEJJI’ATU MA ‘AMILU WE HAKA BIHIM MA KANU BIHI JESTEHZI’UN
  45,34,WE KILEL-JEWME NENSAKUM KEMA NESITUM LIKA’E JEWMIKUM HADHA WE ME’WAKUMU EN-NARU WE MA LEKUM MIN NASIRINE
  45,35,DHALIKUM BI’ENNEKUM ETTEHADHTUM ‘AJATI ELLAHI HUZUEN WE GARRETKUMUL-HEJÆTU ED-DUNJA FALJEWME LA JUHREXHUNE MINHA WE LA HUM JUSTA’TEBUNE
  45,36,FELILLAHIL-HEMDU RABBI ES-SEMAWATI WE RABBIL-’ERDI RABBIL-’ALEMINE
  45,37,WE LEHUL-KIBRIJA’U FI ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI WE HUWEL-’AZIZUL-HEKIMU
  46,1,HA-MIM
  46,2,TENZILUL-KITABI MINEL-LAHIL-’AZIZIL-HEKIMI
  46,3,MA HALEKNA ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDE WE MA BEJNEHUMA ‘ILLA BIL-HEKKI WE ‘EXHELIN MUSEMMEN WEL-LEDHINE KEFERU ‘AMMA ‘UNDHIRU MU’RIDUNE
  46,4,KUL ‘ERE’EJTUM MA TED’UNE MIN DUNI ELLAHI ‘ERUNI MADHA HALEKU MINEL-’ERDI ‘EM LEHUM SHIRKUN FI ES-SEMAWATI EI’TUNI BIKITABIN MIN KABLI HADHA ‘EW ‘ETHARETIN MIN ‘ILMIN ‘IN KUNTUM SADIKINE
  46,5,WE MEN ‘EDELLU MIMMEN JED’U MIN DUNI ELLAHI MEN LA JESTEXHIBU LEHU ‘ILA JEWMIL-KIJAMETI WE HUM ‘AN DU’A’IHIM GAFILUNE
  46,6,WE ‘IDHA HUSHIRE EN-NASU KANU LEHUM ‘A’DA’EN WE KANU BI’IBADETIHIM KAFIRINE
  46,7,WE ‘IDHA TUTLA ‘ALEJHIM ‘AJATUNA BEJJINATIN KALEL-LEDHINE KEFERU LILHEKKI LEMMA XHA’EHUM HADHA SIHRUN MUBINUN
  46,8,‘EM JEKULUNE EFTERAHU KUL ‘INI EFTEREJTUHU FELA TEMLIKUNE LI MINEL-LAHI SHEJ’ÆN HUWE ‘A’LEMU BIMA TUFIDUNE FIHI KEFA BIHI SHEHIDÆN BEJNI WE BEJNEKUM WE HUWEL-GAFURU ER-REHIMU
  46,9,KUL MA KUNTU BID’ÆN MINE ER-RUSULI WE MA ‘EDRI MA JUF’ALU BI WE LA BIKUM ‘IN ‘ETTEBI’U ‘ILLA MA JUHA ‘ILEJJE WE MA ‘ENA ‘ILLA NEDHIRUN MUBINUN
  46,10,KUL ‘ERE’EJTUM ‘IN KANE MIN ‘INDI ELLAHI WE KEFERTUM BIHI WE SHEHIDE SHAHIDUN MIN BENI ‘ISRA’ILE ‘ALA MITHLIHI FE’AMENE WE ESTEKBERTUM ‘INNALL-LLAHE LA JEHDIL-KAWME EDH-DHALIMINE
  46,11,WE KALEL-LEDHINE KEFERU LILLEDHINE ‘AMENU LEW KANE HAJRÆN MA SEBEKUNA ‘ILEJHI WE ‘IDH LEM JEHTEDU BIHI FESEJEKULUNE HADHA ‘IFKUN KADIMUN
  46,12,WE MIN KABLIHI KITABU MUSA ‘IMAMÆN WE REHMETEN WE HEDHA KITABUN MUSEDDIKUN LISANÆN ‘AREBIJÆN LIJUNDHIREL-LEDHINE DHELEMU WE BUSHRA LILMUHSININE
  46,13,‘INNEL-LEDHINE KALU REBBUNALLAHU THUMME ESTEKAMU FELA HAWFUN ‘ALEJHIM WE LA HUM JEHZENUNE
  46,14,‘ULA’IKE ‘ESHABUL-XHENNETI HALIDINE FIHA XHEZA’EN BIMA KANU JA’MELUNE
  46,15,WE WESSEJNAL-’INSANE BIWALIDEJHI ‘IHSANÆN HEMELET/HU ‘UMMUHU KURHÆN WE WEDE’AT/HU KURHÆN WE HEMLUHU WE FISALUHU THELATHUNE SHEHRÆN HETTA ‘IDHA BELEGA ‘ESHUDDEHU WE BELEGA ‘ERBA’INE SENETEN KALE RABBI ‘EWZI’NI ‘EN ‘ESHKURE NI’METEKEL-LETI ‘EN’AMTE ‘ALEJJE
  46,16,‘ULA’IKEL-LEDHINE NETEKABBELU ‘ANHUM ‘EHSENE MA ‘AMILU WE NETEXHAWEZU ‘AN SEJJI’ATIHIM FI ‘ESHABIL-XHENNETI WA’DE ES-SIDKIL-LEDHI KANU JU’ADUNE
  46,17,WEL-LEDHI KALE LIWALIDEJHI ‘UFFIN LEKUMA ‘ETA’IDANINI ‘EN ‘UHREXHE WE KAD HALETIL-KURUNU MIN KABLI WE HUMA JESTEGITHANI ELLAHE WEJLEKE ‘AMIN ‘INNE WA’DEL-LAHI HEKKUN FEJEKULU MA HADHA ‘ILLA ‘ESATIRUL-’EWWELINE
  46,18,‘ULA’IKEL-LEDHINE HEKKA ‘ALEJHIMUL-KAWLU FI ‘UMEMIN KAD HALET MIN KABLIHIM MINEL-XHINNI WEL-’INSI ‘INNEHUM KANU HASIRINE
  46,19,WE LIKULLIN DEREXHATUN MIMMA ‘AMILU WE LIJUWEFFIJEHUM ‘A’MALEHUM WE HUM LA JUDHLEMUNE
  46,20,WE JEWME JU’REDUL-LEDHINE KEFERU ‘ALA EN-NARI ‘EDH/HEBTUM TEJJIBATIKUM FI HEJATIKUMU ED-DUNJA WE ESTEMTA’TUM BIHA FALJEWME TUXHZEWNE ‘ADHABEL-HUNI BIMA KUNTUM TESTEKBIRUNE FIL-’ERDI BIGAJRIL-HEKKI WE BIMA KUNTUM TEFSUKUNE
  46,21,WE EDHKUR ‘EHA ‘ADIN ‘IDH ‘ENDHERE KAWMEHU BIL-’EHKAFI WE KAD HALETI EN-NUDHURU MIN BEJNI JEDEJHI WE MIN HALFIHI ‘ELLA TA’BUDU ‘ILLALLAHE ‘INNI ‘EHAFU ‘ALEJKUM ‘ADHABE JEWMIN ‘ADHIMIN
  46,22,KALU ‘EXHI’TENA LITE’FIKENA ‘AN ‘ALIHETINA FE’TINA BIMA TA’IDUNA ‘IN KUNTE MINE ES-SADIKINE
  46,23,KALE ‘INNEMAL-’ILMU ‘INDEL-LAHI WE ‘UBELLIGUKUM MA ‘URSILTU BIHI WE LEKINNI ‘ERAKUM KAWMÆN TEXHHELUNE
  46,24,FELEMMA RE’EWHU ‘ARIDÆN MUSTEKBILE ‘EWDIJETIHIM KALU HADHA ‘ARIDUN MUMTIRUNA BEL HUWE MA ESTA’XHELTUM BIHI RIHUN FIHA ‘ADHABUN ‘ELIMUN
  46,25,TUDEMMIRU KULLE SHEJ’IN BI’EMRI RABBIHA FE’ESBEHU LA JURA ‘ILLA MESAKINUHUM KEDHALIKE NEXHZIL-KAWMEL-MUXHRIMINE
  46,26,WE LEKAD MEKKENNAHUM FIMA ‘IN MEKKENNAKUM FIHI WE XHE’ALNA LEHUM SEM’ÆN WE ‘EBSARÆN WE ‘EF’IDETEN FEMA ‘EGNA ‘ANHUM SEM’UHUM WE LA ‘EBSARUHUM WE LA ‘EF’IDETUHUM MIN SHEJ’IN ‘IDH KANU JEXHHEDUNE BI’AJATI ELLAHI WE HAKA BIHIM MA KANU BIHI JESTEHZI’UN
  46,27,WE LEKAD ‘EHLEKNA MA HEWLEKUM MINEL-KURA WE SERREFNAL-’AJATI LE’ALLEHUM JERXHI’UNE
  46,28,FELEWLA NESEREHUMUL-LEDHINE ETTEHADHU MIN DUNI ELLAHI KURBANÆN ‘ALIHETEN BEL DELLU ‘ANHUM WE DHELIKE ‘IFKUHUM WE MA KANU JEFTERUNE
  46,29,WE ‘IDH SEREFNA ‘ILEJKE NEFERÆN MINEL-XHINNI JESTEMI’UNEL-KUR’ANE FELEMMA HEDERUHU KALU ‘ENSITU FELEMMA KUDIJE WE LLEW ‘ILA KAWMIHIM MUNDHIRINE
  46,30,KALU JA KAWMENA ‘INNA SEMI’NA KITABÆN ‘UNZILE MIN BA’DI MUSA MUSEDDIKÆN LIMA BEJNE JEDEJHI JEHDI ‘ILAL-HEKKI WE ‘ILA TERIKIN MUSTEKIMIN
  46,31,JA KAWMENA ‘EXHIBU DA’IJEL-LAHI WE ‘AMINU BIHI JEGFIR LEKUM MIN DHUNUBIKUM WE JUXHIRKUM MIN ‘ADHABIN ‘ELIMIN
  46,32,WE MEN LA JUXHIB DA’IJEL-LAHI FELEJSE BIMU’XHIZIN FIL-’ERDI WE LEJSE LEHU MIN DUNIHI ‘EWLIJA’U ‘ULA’IKE FI DELALIN MUBININ
  46,33,‘EWELEM JEREW ‘ENNEL-LAHEL-LEDHI HALEKA ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDE WE LEM JA’JE BIHALKIHINNE BIKADIRIN ‘ALA ‘EN JUHJIJEL-MEWTA BELA ‘INNEHU ‘ALA KULLI SHEJ’IN KADIRUN
  46,34,WE JEWME JU’REDUL-LEDHINE KEFERU ‘ALA EN-NARI ‘ELEJSE HADHA BIL-HEKKI KALU BELA WE RABBINA KALE FEDHUKUL-’ADHABE BIMA KUNTUM TEKFURUNE
  46,35,FASBIR KEMA SEBERE ‘ULUL-’AZMI MINE ER-RUSULI WE LA TESTA’XHIL LEHUM KE’ENNEHUM JEWME JEREWNE MA JU’ADUNE LEM JELBETHU ‘ILLA SA’ATEN MIN NEHARIN BELAGUN FEHEL JUHLEKU ‘ILLAL-KAWMUL-FASIKUNE
  47,1,EL-LEDHINE KEFERU WE SEDDU ‘AN SEBILI ELLAHI ‘EDELLE ‘A’MALEHUM
  47,2,WEL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU WE ‘AMILU ES-SALIHATI WE ‘AMENU BIMA NUZZILE ‘ALA MUHEMMEDIN WE HUWEL-HEKKU MIN RABBIHIM KEFFERE ‘ANHUM SEJJI’ATIHIM WE ‘ESLEHE BALEHUM
  47,3,DHALIKE BI’ENNEL-LEDHINE KEFERU ETTEBA’UL-BATILE WE ‘ENNEL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU ETTEBA’UL-HEKKA MIN RABBIHIM KEDHALIKE JEDRIBU ELLAHU LILNNASI ‘EMTHALEHUM
  47,4,FE’IDHA LEKITUMUL-LEDHINE KEFERU FEDERBE ER-RIKABI HETTA ‘IDHA ‘ETHHANTUMUHUM FESHUDDUL-WETHAKA FE’IMMA MENNÆN BA’DU WE ‘IMMA FIDA’EN HETTA TEDE’AL-HERBU ‘EWZAREHA DHALIKE WE LEW JESHA’U ELLAHU LANTESERE MINHUM WE LEKIN LIJEBLUWE BA’DEKUM BIBA’DIN WEL-LED
  47,5,SEJEHDIHIM WE JUSLIHU BALEHUM
  47,6,WE JUDHILUHUMUL-XHENNETE ‘ARREFEHA LEHUM
  47,7,JA ‘EJJUHAL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU ‘IN TENSURU ELLAHE JENSURKUM WE JUTHEBBIT ‘EKDAMEKUM
  47,8,WEL-LEDHINE KEFERU FETA’SÆN LEHUM WE ‘EDELLE ‘A’MALEHUM
  47,9,DHALIKE BI’ENNEHUM KERIHU MA ‘ENZELEL-LAHU FE’EHBETE ‘A’MALEHUM
  47,10,‘EFELEM JESIRU FIL-’ERDI FEJENDHURU KEJFE KANE ‘AKIBETUL-LEDHINE MIN KABLIHIM DEMMEREL-LAHU ‘ALEJHIM WE LILKAFIRINE ‘EMTHALUHA
  47,11,DHALIKE BI’ENNEL-LAHE MEWLAL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU WE ‘ENNEL-KAFIRINE LA MEWLA LEHUM
  47,12,‘INNALL-LLAHE JUDHILUL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU WE ‘AMILU ES-SALIHATI XHENNATIN TEXHRI MIN TEHTIHAL-’ENHARU WEL-LEDHINE KEFERU JETEMETTA’UNE WE JE’KULUNE KEMA TE’KULUL-’EN’AM WE EN-NARU METHWEN LEHUM
  47,13,WE KE’EJJIN MIN KARJETIN HIJE ‘ESHEDDU KUWETEN MIN KARJETIKEL-LETI ‘EHREXHETKE ‘EHLEKNAHUM FELA NASIRE LEHUM
  47,14,‘EFEMEN KANE ‘ALA BEJJINETIN MIN RABBIHI KEMEN ZUJJINE LEHU SU’U ‘AMELIHI WE ETTEBA’U ‘EHWA’EHUM
  47,15,METHELUL-XHENNETI ELLETI WU’IDEL-MUTTEKUNE FIHA ‘ENHARUN MIN MA’IN GAJRI ‘ASININ WE ‘ENHARUN MIN LEBENIN LEM JETEGAJJER TA’MUHU WE ‘ENHARUN MIN HAMRIN LEDHDHETIN LILSHSHARIBINE WE ‘ENHARUN MIN ‘ASELIN MUSEFFEN WE LEHUM FIHA MIN KULLI ETH-THEMERATI WE MEGF
  47,16,WE MINHUM MEN JESTEMI’U ‘ILEJKE HETTA ‘IDHA HAREXHU MIN ‘INDIKE KALU LILLEDHINE ‘UTUL-’ILME MADHA KALE ‘ANIFÆN ‘ULA’IKEL-LEDHINE TEBE’ALLAHU ‘ALA KULUBIHIM WE ETTEBA’U ‘EHWA’EHUM
  47,17,WEL-LEDHINE EHTEDEW ZADEHUM HUDEN WE ‘ATAHUM TEKWHUM
  47,18,FEHEL JENDHURUNE ‘ILLA ES-SA’ATE ‘EN TE’TIJEHUM BEGTETEN FEKAD XHA’E ‘ESHRATUHA FE’ENNA LEHUM ‘IDHA XHA’ET/HUM DHIKRAHUM
  47,19,FA’LEM ‘ENNEHU LA ‘ILAHE ‘ILLALLAHU WE ESTEGFIR LIDHENBIKE WE LILMU’UMININE WEL-MU’UMINATI WEL-LAHU JA’LEMU MUTEKALLEBEKUM WE METHWAKUM
  47,20,WE JEKULUL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU LEWLA NUZZILET SURETUN FE’IDHA ‘UNZILET SURETUN MUHKEMETUN WE DHUKIRE FIHAL-KITALU RE’EJTEL-LEDHINE FI KULUBIHIM MEREDUN JENDHURUNE ‘ILEJKE NEDHEREL-MEGSHIJI ‘ALEJHI MINEL-MEWTI FE’EWLA LEHUM
  47,21,TA’ATUN WE KAWLUN MA’RUFUN FE’IDHA ‘AZEMEL-’EMRU FELEW SEDEKU ELLAHE LEKANE HAJRÆN LEHUM
  47,22,FEHEL ‘ASEJTUM ‘IN TEWELLEJTUM ‘EN TUFSIDU FIL-’ERDI WE TUKATTI’U ‘ERHAMEKUM
  47,23,‘ULA’IKEL-LEDHINE LE’ANEHUMU ELLAHU FE’ESEMMEHUM WE ‘A’MA ‘EBSAREHUM
  47,24,‘EFELA JETEDEBBERUNEL-KUR’ANE ‘EM ‘ALA KULUBIN ‘EKFALUHA
  47,25,‘INNEL-LEDHINE ERTEDDU ‘ALA ‘EDBARIHIM MIN BA’DI MA TEBEJJENE LEHUMUL-HUDA ESH-SHEJTANU SEWWELE LEHUM WE ‘EMLA LEHUM
  47,26,DHALIKE BI’ENNEHUM KALU LILLEDHINE KERIHU MA NEZZELEL-LAHU SENUTI’UKUM FI BA’DIL-’EMRI WEL-LAHU JA’LEMU ‘ISRAREHUM
  47,27,FEKEJFE ‘IDHA TEWEFFET/HUMUL-MELA’IKETU JEDRIBUNE WUXHUHEHUM WE ‘EDBAREHUM
  47,28,DHALIKE BI’ENNEHUMU ETTEBA’U MA ‘ESHATEL-LAHE WE KERIHU RIDWANEHU FE’EHBETE ‘A’MALEHUM
  47,29,‘EM HESIBEL-LEDHINE FI KULUBIHIM MEREDUN ‘EN LEN JUHRIXHEL-LAHU ‘EDGANEHUM
  47,30,WE LEW NESHA’U LE’EREJNAKEHUM FELE’AREFTEHUM BISIMAHUM WE LETA’RIFENNEHUM FI LEHNIL-KAWLI WEL-LAHU JA’LEMU ‘A’MALEKUM
  47,31,WE LENEBLUWENNEKUM HETTA NA’LEMEL-MUXHAHIDINE MINKUM WE ES-SABIRINE WE NEBLUWE ‘EHBAREKUM
  47,32,‘INNEL-LEDHINE KEFERU WE SEDDU ‘AN SEBILI ELLAHI WE SHAKKU ER-RESULE MIN BA’DI MA TEBEJJENE LEHUMUL-HUDA LEN JEDURRU ELLAHE SHEJ’ÆN WE SEJUHBITU ‘A’MALEHUM
  47,33,JA ‘EJJUHAL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU ‘ETI’U ELLAHE WE ‘ETI’U ER-RESULE WE LA TUBTILU ‘A’MALEKUM
  47,34,‘INNEL-LEDHINE KEFERU WE SEDDU ‘AN SEBILI ELLAHI THUMME MATU WE HUM KUFFARUN FELEN JEGFIREL-LAHU LEHUM
  47,35,FELA TEHINU WE TED’U ‘ILA ES-SELMI WE ‘ENTUMUL-’A’LEWNE WEL-LAHU ME’AKUM WE LEN JETIREKUM ‘A’MALEKUM
  47,36,‘INNEMAL-HEJÆTU ED-DUNJA LA’IBUN WE LEHWUN WE ‘IN TU’UMINU WE TETTEKU JU’UTIKUM ‘UXHUREKUM WE LA JES’ELKUM ‘EMWALEKUM
  47,37,‘IN JES’ELKUMUHA FEJUHFIKUM TEBHALU WE JUHRIXH ‘EDGANEKUM
  47,38,HA’ENTUM HA’UULA’ TUD’AWNE LITUNFIKU FI SEBILI ELLAHI FEMINKUM MEN JEBHALU WE MEN JEBHAL FE’INNEMA JEBHALU ‘AN NEFSIHI WEL-LAHUL-GANIJU WE ‘ENTUMUL-FUKARA’U WE ‘IN TETEWELLEW JESTEBDIL KAWMÆN GAJREKUM THUMME LA JEKUNU ‘EMTHALEKUM
  48,1,‘INNA FETEHNA LEKE FETHÆN MUBINÆN
  48,2,LIJEGFIRE LEKEL-LAHU MA TEKADDEME MIN DHENBIKE WE MA TE’EHHARE WE JUTIMME NI’METEHU ‘ALEJKE WE JEHDIJEKE SIRATÆN MUSTEKIMÆN
  48,3,WE JENSUREKEL-LAHU NESRÆN ‘AZIZÆN
  48,4,HUWEL-LEDHI ‘ENZELE ES-SEKINETE FI KULUBIL-MU’UMININE LIJEZDADU ‘IMANÆN ME’A ‘IMANIHIM WE LILLEHI XHUNUDU ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI WE KANEL-LAHU ‘ALIMÆN HEKIMÆN
  48,5,LIJUDHILEL-MU’UMININE WEL-MU’UMINATI XHENNATIN TEXHRI MIN TEHTIHAL-’ENHARU HALIDINE FIHA WE JUKEFFIRE ‘ANHUM SEJJI’ATIHIM WE KANE DHALIKE ‘INDEL-LAHI FEWZÆN ‘ADHIMÆN
  48,6,WE JU’ADHDHIBEL-MUNAFIKINE WEL-MUNAFIKATI WEL-MUSHRIKINE WEL-MUSHRIKATI EDH-DHANNINE BILLAHI DHENNE ES-SEW’I ‘ALEJHIM DA’IRETU ES-SEW’I WE GADIBEL-LAHU ‘ALEJHIM WE LE’ANEHUM WE ‘E’ADDE LEHUM XHEHENNEME WE SA’ET MESIRÆN
  48,7,WE LILLEHI XHUNUDU ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI WE KANEL-LAHU ‘AZIZÆN HEKIMÆN
  48,8,‘INNA ‘ERSELNAKE SHAHIDÆN WE MUBESHSHIRÆN WE NEDHIRÆN
  48,9,LITU’UMINU BILLAHI WE RESULIHI WE TU’AZZIRUHU WE TUWEKKIRUHU WE TUSEBBIHUHU BUKRETEN WE ‘ESILÆN
  48,10,‘INNEL-LEDHINE JUBAJI’UNEKE ‘INNEMA JUBAJI’UNEL-LAHE JEDU ELLAHI FEWKA ‘EJDIHIM FEMEN NEKETHE FE’INNEMA JENKUTHU ‘ALA NEFSIHI WE MEN ‘EWFA BIMA ‘AHEDE ‘ALEJHU ELLAHE FESEJU’UTIHI ‘EXHRÆN ‘ADHIMÆN
  48,11,SEJEKULU LEKEL-MUHALLEFUNE MINEL-’A’RABI SHEGALETNA ‘EMWALUNA WE ‘EHLUNA FASTEGFIR LENA JEKULUNE BI’ELSINETIHIM MA LEJSE FI KULUBIHIM KUL FEMEN JEMLIKU LEKUM MINEL-LAHI SHEJ’ÆN ‘IN ‘ERADE BIKUM DERRÆN ‘EW ‘ERADE BIKUM NEF’ÆN BEL KANEL-LAHU BIMA TA’MELUNE
  48,12,BEL DHENENTUM ‘EN LEN JENKALIBE ER-RESULU WEL-MU’UMINUNE ‘ILA ‘EHLIHIM ‘EBEDÆN WE ZUJJINE DHALIKE FI KULUBIKUM WE DHENENTUM DHENNE ES-SEW’I WE KUNTUM KAWMÆN BURÆN
  48,13,WE MEN LEM JU’UMIN BILLAHI WE RESULIHI FE’INNA ‘A’TEDNA LILKAFIRINE SA’IRÆN
  48,14,WE LILLEHI MULKU ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI JEGFIRU LIMEN JESHA’U WE JU’ADHDHIBU MEN JESHA’U WE KANEL-LAHU GAFURÆN REHIMÆN
  48,15,SEJEKULUL-MUHALLEFUNE ‘IDHA ENTELEKTUM ‘ILA MEGANIME LITE’HUDHUHA DHERUNA NETTEBI’KUM JURIDUNE ‘EN JUBEDDILU KELAMEL-LAHI KUL LEN TETTEBI’UNA KEDHALIKUM KALEL-LAHU MIN KABLU FESEJEKULUNE BEL TEHSUDUNENA BEL KANU LA JEFKAHUNE ‘ILLA KALILÆN
  48,16,KUL LILMUHALLEFINE MINEL-’A’RABI SETUD’AWNE ‘ILA KAWMIN ‘ULI BE’SIN SHEDIDIN TUKATILUNEHUM ‘EW JUSLIMUNE FE’IN TUTI’U JU’UTIKUMU ELLAHU ‘EXHRÆN HESENÆN WE ‘IN TETEWELLEW KEMA TEWELLEJTUM MIN KABLU JU’ADHDHIBKUM ‘ADHABÆN ‘ELIMÆN
  48,17,LEJSE ‘ALEL-’A’MA HEREXHUN WE LA ‘ALEL-’A’REXHI HEREXHUN WE LA ‘ALEL-MERIDI HEREXHUN WE MEN JUTI’I ELLAHE WE RESULEHU JUDHILHU XHENNATIN TEXHRI MIN TEHTIHAL-’ENHARU WE MEN JETEWELLE JU’ADHDHIBHU ‘ADHABÆN ‘ELIMÆN
  48,18,LEKAD REDIJEL-LAHU ‘ANIL-MU’UMININE ‘IDH JUBAJI’UNEKE TEHTE ESH-SHEXHERETI FE’ALIME MA FI KULUBIHIM FE’ENZELE ES-SEKINETE ‘ALEJHIM WE ‘ETHABEHUM FETHÆN KARIBÆN
  48,19,WE MEGANIME KETHIRETEN JE’HUDHUNEHA WE KANEL-LAHU ‘AZIZÆN HEKIMÆN
  48,20,WE’ADEKUMU ELLAHU MEGANIME KETHIRETEN TE’HUDHUNEHA FE’AXHXHELE LEKUM HEDHIHI WE KEFFE ‘EJDIJE EN-NASI ‘ANKUM WE LITEKUNE ‘AJETEN LILMU’UMININE WE JEHDIJEKUM SIRATÆN MUSTEKIMÆN
  48,21,WE ‘UHRA LEM TEKDIRU ‘ALEJHA KAD ‘EHATEL-LAHU BIHA WE KANEL-LAHU ‘ALA KULLI SHEJ’IN KADIRÆN
  48,22,WE LEW KATELEKUMUL-LEDHINE KEFERU LEWELLEWL-’EDBARE THUMME LA JEXHIDUNE WELIJÆN WE LA NESIRÆN
  48,23,SUNNETEL-LAHI ELLETI KAD HALET MIN KABLU WE LEN TEXHIDE LISUNNETI ELLAHI TEBDILÆN
  48,24,WE HUWEL-LEDHI KEFFE ‘EJDIJEHUM ‘ANKUM WE ‘EJDIJEKUM ‘ANHUM BIBETNI MEKKETE MIN BA’DI ‘EN ‘EDHFEREKUM ‘ALEJHIM WE KANEL-LAHU BIMA TA’MELUNE BESIRÆN
  48,25,HUMUL-LEDHINE KEFERU WE SEDDUKUM ‘ANIL-MESXHIDIL-HERAMI WEL-HEDJE MA’KUFÆN ‘EN JEBLUGA MEHILLEHU WE LEWLA RIXHALUN MU’UMINUNE WE NISA’UN MU’UMINATUN LEM TA’LEMUHUM ‘EN TETE’UHUM FETUSIBEKUM MINHUM ME’ARRETUN BIGAJRI ‘ILMIN LIJUDHILEL-LAHU FI REHMETIHI MEN
  48,26,‘IDH XHE’ALEL-LEDHINE KEFERU FI KULUBIHIMUL-HEMIJETE HEMIJETEL-XHAHILIJETI FE’ENZELEL-LAHU SEKINETEHU ‘ALA RESULIHI WE ‘ALEL-MU’UMININE WE ‘ELZEMEHUM KELIMETET-TEKWA WE KANU ‘EHEKKA BIHA WE ‘EHLEHA WE KANEL-LAHU BIKULLI SHEJ’IN ‘ALIMÆN
  48,27,LEKAD SEDEKAL-LAHU RESULEHU ER-RU’UJA BIL-HEKKI LETEDHULUNNEL-MESXHIDEL-HERAME ‘IN SHA’EL-LAHU ‘AMININE MUHELLIKINE RU’USEKUM WE MUKASSIRINE LA TEHAFUNE FE’ALIME MA LEM TA’LEMU FEXHE’ALE MIN DUNI DHALIKE FETHÆN KARIBÆN
  48,28,HUWEL-LEDHI ‘ERSELE RESULEHU BIL-HUDA WE DINIL-HEKKI LIJUDHHIREHU ‘ALA ED-DINI KULLIHI WE KEFA BILLAHI SHEHIDÆN
  48,29,MUHEMMEDUN RESULU ELLAHI WEL-LEDHINE ME’AHU ‘ESHIDDA’U ‘ALEL-KUFFARI RUHEMA’U BEJNEHUM TERAHUM RUKKA’ÆN SUXHXHEDÆN JEBTEGUNE FEDLÆN MINEL-LAHI WE RIDWANÆN SIMAHUM FI WUXHUHIHIM MIN ‘ETHERI ES-SUXHUDI DHALIKE METHELUHUM FIT-TEWRÆTI WE METHELUHUM FIL-’INXHI
  49,1,JA ‘EJJUHAL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU LA TUKADDIMU BEJNE JEDEJI ELLAHI WE RESULIHI WE ETTEKU ELLAHE ‘INNALL-LLAHE SEMI’UN ‘ALIMUN
  49,2,JA ‘EJJUHAL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU LA TERFA’U ‘ESWATEKUM FEWKA SEWTI EN-NEBIJI WE LA TEXHHERU LEHU BIL-KAWLI KEXHEHRI BA’DIKUM LIBA’DIN ‘EN TEHBETE ‘A’MALUKUM WE ‘ENTUM LA TESH’URUNE
  49,3,‘INNEL-LEDHINE JEGUDDUNE ‘ESWATEHUM ‘INDE RESULI ELLAHI ‘ULA’IKEL-LEDHINE EMTEHENEL-LAHU KULUBEHUM LILTTEKWA LEHUM MEGFIRETUN WE ‘EXHRUN ‘ADHIMUN
  49,4,‘INNEL-LEDHINE JUNADUNEKE MIN WERA’IL-HUXHURATI ‘EKTHERUHUM LA JA’KILUNE
  49,5,WE LEW ‘ENNEHUM SEBERU HETTA TEHRUXHE ‘ILEJHIM LEKANE HAJRÆN LEHUM WEL-LAHU GAFURUN REHIMUN
  49,6,JA ‘EJJUHAL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU ‘IN XHA’EKUM FASIKUN BINEBE’IIN FETEBEJJENU ‘EN TUSIBU KAWMÆN BIXHEHALETIN FETUSBIHU ‘ALA MA FE’ALTUM NADIMINE
  49,7,WE A’LEMU ‘ENNE FIKUM RESULEL-LAHI LEW JUTI’UKUM FI KETHIRIN MINEL-’EMRI LE’ANITTUM WE LEKINNALL-LLAHE HEBBEBE ‘ILEJKUMUL-’IMANE WE ZEJJENEHU FI KULUBIKUM WE KERREHE ‘ILEJKUMUL-KUFRE WEL-FUSUKA WEL-’ISJANE ‘ULA’IKE HUMU ER-RASHIDUNE
  49,8,FEDLÆN MINEL-LAHI WE NI’METEN WEL-LAHU ‘ALIMUN HEKIMUN
  49,9,WE ‘IN TA’IFETANI MINEL-MU’UMININE EKTETELU FE’ESLIHU BEJNEHUMA FE’IN BEGAT ‘IHDAHUMA ‘ALEL-’UHRA FEKATILU ELLETI TEBGI HETTA TEFI’E ‘ILA ‘EMRI ELLAHI FE’IN FA’ET FE’ESLIHU BEJNEHUMA BIL-’ADLI WE ‘EKSITU ‘INNALL-LLAHE JUHIBBUL-MUKSITINE
  49,10,‘INNEMAL-MU’UMINUNE ‘IHWETUN FE’ESLIHU BEJNE ‘EHAWEJKUM WE ETTEKU ELLAHE LE’ALLEKUM TURHEMUNE
  49,11,JA ‘EJJUHAL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU LA JESHAR KAWMUN MIN KAWMIN ‘ASA ‘EN JEKUNU HAJRÆN MINHUM WE LA NISA’UN MIN NISA’IN ‘ASA ‘EN JEKUNNE HAJRÆN MINHUNNE WE LA TELMIZU ‘ENFUSEKUM WE LA TENABEZU BIL-’ELKABI BI’SEL-EISMUL-FUSUKU BA’DEL-’IMANI WE MEN LEM JETUB FE’ULA’
  49,12,JA ‘EJJUHAL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU EXHTENIBU KETHIRÆN MINE EDH-DHENNI ‘INNE BA’DE EDH-DHENNI ‘ITHMUN WE LA TEXHESSESU WE LA JEGTEB BA’DUKUM BA’DÆN ‘EJUHIBBU ‘EHEDUKUM ‘EN JE’KULE LEHME ‘EHIHI MEJTÆN FEKERIHTUMUHU WE ETTEKU ELLAHE ‘INNALL-LLAHE TEWWABUN REHIMUN
  49,13,JA ‘EJJUHA EN-NASU ‘INNA HALEKNAKUM MIN DHEKERIN WE ‘UNTHA WE XHE’ALNAKUM SHU’UBÆN WE KABA’ILE LITA’AREFU ‘INNE ‘EKREMEKUM ‘INDEL-LAHI ‘ETKAKUM ‘INNALL-LLAHE ‘ALIMUN HABIRUN
  49,14,KALETIL-’A’RABU ‘AMENNA KUL LEM TU’UMINU WE LEKIN KULU ‘ESLEMNA WE LEMMA JEDHULIL-’IMANU FI KULUBIKUM WE ‘IN TUTI’U ELLAHE WE RESULEHU LA JELITKUM MIN ‘A’MALIKUM SHEJ’ÆN ‘INNALL-LLAHE GAFURUN REHIMUN
  49,15,‘INNEMAL-MU’UMINUNEL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU BILLAHI WE RESULIHI THUMME LEM JERTABU WE XHAHEDU BI’EMWALIHIM WE ‘ENFUSIHIM FI SEBILI ELLAHI ‘ULA’IKE HUMU ES-SADIKUNE
  49,16,KUL ‘ETU’ALLIMUNEL-LAHE BIDINIKUM WEL-LAHU JA’LEMU MA FI ES-SEMAWATI WE MA FIL-’ERDI WEL-LAHU BIKULLI SHEJ’IN ‘ALIMUN
  49,17,JEMUNNUNE ‘ALEJKE ‘EN ‘ESLEMU KUL LA TEMUNNU ‘ALEJJE ‘ISLAMEKUM BELI ELLAHU JEMUNNU ‘ALEJKUM ‘EN HEDAKUM LIL’IMANI ‘IN KUNTUM SADIKINE
  49,18,‘INNALL-LLAHE JA’LEMU GAJBE ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI WEL-LAHU BESIRUN BIMA TA’MELUNE